%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Believe%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20Explanation%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%3B%20It%E2%80%99s%20Absolutely%20Ridiculous'%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05135228%2FKT-B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20share%20his%20immediate%20response%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fstate-bank-of-india-extra-time-june-30-electoral-bonds-supreme-court%5C%22%3EState%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20petition%20requesting%20more%20than%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%20extra%20time%20till%20June%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20public%20electoral%20bond%20details%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20most%20respected%20former%20judges%20has%20said%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20the%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20explanation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Deepak%20Gupta%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20part%20of%20a%20bench%20which%20in%202019%20had%20told%20the%20SBI%20to%20collate%20and%20keep%20the%20relevant%20details%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20i.e.%20to%20maintain%20records%20and%20he%20does%20not%20accept%20that%20they%20now%20need%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%20extra%20time%20(over%20and%20above%20the%20initial%20three%20weeks%20granted%20to%20them)%20to%20make%20the%20information%20available%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20in%20the%20interview%20he%20said%20the%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20position%20was%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20ridiculous%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gupta%20also%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20explanation%20is%20not%20really%20worth%20much%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FL-qdDu1N3i8%3Fsi%3D9Dep7gFuQVuCYta0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%