20advisory%20has%20suddenly%20been%20issued%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20for%20Information%20Technology%2C%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%2C%20too%2C%20rushed%20to%20list%20out%20exceptions%20for%20the%20advisory%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%20He%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20apply%20to%20any%20platforms%20working%20in%20the%20healthcare%20or%20agriculture%20sector.%20It%20will%20apply%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology%2Fai-models-must-take-permission-before-launching-to-indian-public-says-government-12388631.html%5C%22%3Ereported%20moneycontrol.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20clarified%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20missive%20was%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Cregulatory%20framework%E2%80%9D%20but%20an%20advisory%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctest%20your%20model%20before%20launching%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology%2Fai-models-must-take-permission-before-launching-to-indian-public-says-government-12388631.html%5C%22%3Eadvisory%20issued%20to%20intermediaries%20on%20March%201%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20IT%20ministry%20had%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cexplicit%20permission%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20government%20was%20necessary%20to%20deploy%20AI%20models%20in%20testing%20stage.%20The%20advisory%20also%20ordered%20platforms%20%E2%80%9Cto%20label%20synthetic%20content%20with%20unique%20identifiers%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20identify%20the%20creator%20of%20misinformation%20or%20deepfake.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fai-artificial-intelligence-advisory-rajeev-chandrasekhar%5C%22%3EAs%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Modi%20a%20Fascist%3F%E2%80%9D%20answered%20with%20certainty%20by%20Google%20Gemini%20first%20caused%20a%20storm%20and%20suggested%20a%20complete%20chan