%2C%20he%20has%20another%20revelation%3A%20his%20purpose%20in%20life%20is%20not%20to%20live%20the%20humble%20life%20of%20a%20monk%20but%20to%20use%20his%20preternatural%20oratory%20skills%20to%20share%20wisdom%20with%20the%20world.%20Thus%20begins%20his%20transformation%20into%20a%20public%20self-help%20personality%20and%20his%20swift%20rise%20to%20fame.%20Shetty's%20success%20is%20largely%20predicated%20on%20this%20riches-to-rags-to-riches%20backstory%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20the%20veracity%20of%20Jay%20Shetty's%20story%2C%20the%20report%20added%2C%20%26quot%3B%C2%A0But%20people%20close%20to%20Shetty%20have%20questioned%20whether%20his%20conversion%20to%20a%20life%20of%20monkhood%20was%20quite%20so%20dramatic.%20Much%20of%20Shetty's%20spiritual%20education%20took%20place%20not%20in%20India%20but%20in%20Watford%2C%20an%20orbital%20town%20outside%20north-west%20London%2C%20they%20say.%20He%20was%20there%20not%20because%20of%20spiritual%20discovery%20in%20college%20but%20because%20he%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20International%20Society%20for%20Krishna%20Consciousness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20daily%20newspaper%C2%A0also%C2%A0questioned%20Mr%20Shetty's%20academic%20qualifications%2C%20pointing%20out%20discrepancies%20in%20his%20resume%2C%20including%20a%20degree%20from%20a%20business%20school%20that%20does%20not%20offer%20the%20claimed%20course.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CShetty%20is%20hardly%20the%20first%20self-help%20guru%20to%20embellish%20his%20spiritual%20credentials%20to%20amass%20followers%2C%20but%20he%20demands%20huge%20sums%20of%20money%20for%20his%20guidance.%20Shetty%20has%20used%20his%20spiritual%20authority%20to%20launch%20a%20number%20of%20subscription%20and%20education%20services%2C%20including%20the%20life-coaching%20school%2C%20which%20charges%20%247%2C400%20a%20term%20for%20%E2%80%98Postgraduate%20Diploma%20(Level%207)%20qualifications'%20%E2%80%93%20equivalent%20to%