eached%20the%20Maldives%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20one%20of%20the%20three%20aviation%20platforms%20in%20the%20island%20nation%2C%20well%20ahead%20of%20the%20March%2010%20deadline%20agreed%20by%20the%20two%20nations%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20Baa%20atoll%20Eydhafushi%20residential%20community%20during%20his%20tour%20across%20the%20atoll%2C%20the%20President%20stated%20that%20due%20to%20his%20government's%20success%20in%20expelling%20Indian%20troops%20from%20the%20country%2C%20people%20who%20spread%20false%20rumours%2C%20are%20attempting%20to%20twist%20the%20situation%2C%20a%20news%20portal%20Edition.mv%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20these%20people%20%5BIndian%20military%5D%20are%20not%20departing%2C%20that%20they%20are%20returning%20after%20changing%20their%20uniforms%20into%20civilian%20clothing.%20We%20must%20not%20indulge%20such%20thoughts%20that%20instil%20doubts%20in%20our%20hearts%20and%20spread%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20portal%20quoted%20Mr%20Muizzu%2C%20widely%20regarded%20as%20a%20China-backed%20leader%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20Indian%20troops%20in%20the%20country%20come%20May%2010.%20Not%20in%20uniform%20and%20not%20in%20civilian%20clothing.%20The%20Indian%20military%20will%20not%20be%20residing%20in%20this%20country%20in%20any%20form%20of%20clothing.%20I%20state%20this%20with%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20on%20a%20day%20when%20his%20country%20signed%20an%20agreement%20with%20China%20to%20receive%20free%20military%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20last%20month%2C%20after%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20on%20February%202%20between%20the%20two%20sides%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20India%20would%20replace%20its%20military%20personnel%20operating%20the%20three%20aviation%20platforms%20in%20the%20Maldives%20by%20May%2010%20and%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20process%20would%20be%20completed%20by%20March%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20maiden%20address%20to%20Parliament%20on%20February%205%2C%20he%20made%20similar%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2088%20military%20personnel%20manning%20the%20three%20Indian%20platforms%20that%20have%20been%20providing%20humanitarian%20and%20medical%20evacuation%20services%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Maldives%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years%20using%20two%20helicopters%20and%20a%20Dornier%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Muizzu%20rode%20to%20power%20last%20year%20on%20an%20anti-India%20stance%20and%20within%20hours%20of%20taking%20oath%20demanded%20India%20to%20remove%20its%20personnel%20from%20the%20strategically%20located%20archipelago%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEdition.mv%20further%20reported%20that%20while%20the%20first%20troops%20to%20depart%20the%20country%20are%20the%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20operating%20the%20two%20helicopters%20in%20Addu%20City%2C%20the%20military%20personnel%20present%20in%20Haa%20Dhaalu%20atoll%20Hanimaadhoo%20and%20Laamu%20atoll%20Kahdhoo%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20leave%20ahead%20of%20May%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20agreed%20to%20remove%20their%20troops%20from%20Maldives%20under%20the%20condition%20that%20a%20number%20of%20their%20civilians%20equivalent%20to%20the%20military%20presence%20are%20brought%20to%20operate%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20been%20directing%20criticism%20at%20the%20administration%20asserting%20that%20the%20Indian%20personnel%20sent%20to%20Maldives%20as%20civilians%20are%20in%20reality%20military%20officials%20out%20of%20uniform%20and%20that%20the%20government%20has%20no%20way%20to%20ascertain%20otherwise%2C%20the%20portal%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20local%20media%20reports%20also%20said%20that%20Maldives%20has%20successfully%20tied%20up%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20run%20flights%20for%20medical%20evacuation%20last%20week%2C%20further%20indicating%20that%20it%20is%20bent%20on%20removing%20all%20Indian%20troops%20in%20whichever%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20highlighting%20that%20securing%20true%20independence%20is%20a%20concept%20he%20regards%20with%20utmost%20priority%2C%20the%20President%20remarked%20that%20the%20State%20is%20exerting%20efforts%20with%20due%20importance%20%26quot%3Bto%20regain%20the%20southern%20maritime%20area%20deprived%20of%20the%20country%20in%20addition%20to%20expelling%20Indian%20troops%20from%20the%20Maldives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20we%20can%20achieve%20this.%20The%20delay%20in%20concluding%20this%20task%20is%20due%20to%20the%20adverse%20procedures%20practiced%20during%20the%20implementation.%20It%20was%20done%20without%20even%20taking%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20parliament%20...%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Constitution%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20portal%20quoted%20the%20President%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives'%20proximity%20to%20India%2C%20barely%2070%20nautical%20miles%20from%20the%20island%20of%20Minicoy%20in%20Lakshadweep%20and%20300%20nautical%20miles%20from%20the%20mainland's%20western%20coast%2C%20and%20its%20location%20at%20the%20hub%20of%20commercial%20sea%20lanes%20running%20through%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20(IOR)%20gives%20it%20significant%20strategic%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20has%20been%20India's%20key%20maritime%20neighbour%20in%20the%20IOR%20and%20it%20occupies%20a%20special%20place%20in%20its%20initiatives%20such%20as%20SAGAR%20(Security%20and%20Growth%20for%20All%20in%20the%20Region)%20and%20the%20Neighbourhood%20First%20Policy.'%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709623560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fqj88pb58_moha