esperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%2C%20to%20which%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20said%20lot%20of%20things%20against%20me%20as%20a%20political%20spokesperson%2C%20but%20I%20like%20him%20as%20a%20person.%20He%20is%20a%20good%20human%20being%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20interview%20about%20the%20bribery%20case%20he%20was%20hearing%20-%20in%20connection%20with%20which%20Supreme%20Court%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20%26quot%3Bjudges%20have%20no%20business%20granting%20interviews%20on%20pending%20matters%26quot%3B%20-%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%20has%20frequently%20made%20headlines%20with%20rulings%20on%20various%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20earlier%20this%20year%20he%20accused%20Justice%20Soumen%20Sen%20-%20who%20led%20a%20bench%20that%20stayed%20an%20order%20for%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20college%20irregularities%20-%20of%20working%20for%20a%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20is%20pending%20in%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-stays-calcutta-high-court-judge-abhijit-gangopadhyays-order-of-cbi-probe-into-medical-admission-irregularities-4940596%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20Judge%20vs%20Judge%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Stays%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcalcutta-high-court-justice-abhijit-gangopadhyay-bars-boycott-call-after-calcutta-high-court-judge-orders-lawyers-arrest-4701254%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr%20Gangopadhyay's%20order%20to%20arrest%20a%20lawyer%20in%20the%20courtroom%20on%20contempt%20charges%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20bar%20association%20adamant%20on%20boycotting%20all%20proceedings%20involving%20the%20judge.%20He%20was%20hearing%20a%20case%20related%20to%20the%20state's%20Madrasah%20Ser