litary%20forces.%20The%20saffron%20party%20has%20also%20mobilised%20its%20leaders%20and%20workers%20in%20Kashmir%20to%20make%20the%20event%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgrand%20success%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20J%26amp%3BK%20spokesperson%20Altaf%20Thakur%20said%20that%20the%20party%20was%20going%20to%20install%2010%2C000%20BJP%20flags%20across%20Srinagar%20city%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20crossings%20and%20entry%2Fexit%20points%20in%20Srinagar%20will%20be%20covered%20by%20the%20BJP%20flags%20and%20banners%20because%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20popular%20leader%20and%20our%20torchbearer%20PM%20Modi%20is%20going%20to%20address%20the%20rally.%20Not%20just%20the%20workers%20but%20our%20leaders%20also%20are%20on%20the%20road%20to%20welcome%20the%20PM%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Modi%20addressed%20a%20rally%20in%20Jammu%20where%20he%20inaugurated%20developmental%20initiatives%20worth%20over%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore.%20The%20party%20has%20renominated%20its%20two%20sitting%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20%E2%80%93%20Jitendra%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%2C%20and%20Jugal%20Kishore%20%E2%80%93%20as%20its%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Udhampur%20and%20Jammu%20seats%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709621697000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08160332%2FH20220203107835.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnarendra-modi-kashmir-srinagar-govt-employees%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rally%20will%20be%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20first%20in%20Srinagar%20in%20nine%20years%20and%20it%20will%20also%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Kashmir.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%