%3EDoctors%20had%20to%20amputate%20Sherri's%20arms%20and%20legs%20below%20the%20elbows%20and%20knees%20after%20saving%20her%20life.%20After%20the%20amputations%20in%20June%202023%2C%20she%20returned%20home%20in%20August.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20is%20now%20caring%20full-time%20for%20his%20wife%20and%20has%20left%20his%20job.%20The%20couple%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20choose%20happiness%20over%20hardships.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20choose%20to%20be%20happy.%20It's%20not%20to%20say%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20breakdown%20every%20now%20and%20then%20and%20just%20cry%20a%20little%20bit.%20I%20don't%20let%20it%20last%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Sherri%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20just%20amazing.%20I've%20had%20more%20struggles.%20Both%20of%20us%20together%20talk%20about%20our%20blessings.%20We%20talk%20about%20the%20things%20that%20are%20going%20right%20in%20our%20day%2C%20in%20our%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709619540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F6sdjk918_sherri-moody_625x300_05_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teachers-limbs-mummified-by-infection-forced-to-undergo-amputation-5179258%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sherri's%20body's%20resistance%20to%20infection%20was%20weakened%20by%20the%20arthritis%20medicine%20she%20was%20taking%2C%20which%20made%20the%20situation%20worse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teachers-limbs-mummified-by-infection-forced-to-undergo-amputation-5179258%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teachers-limbs-mummified-by-infection-forced-to-undergo-amputation-5179258%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teachers-limbs-mummified-by-infection-forced-to-undergo-amputation-5179258%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%