0Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fhan-so-hees-agency-issues-clarification-on-her-controversial-video-from-paris-brand-party%2Farticleshow%2F108226588.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stage%20Performer%20Gangraped%20In%20Jharkhand%2C%20Days%20After%20Spanish%20Woman%20Assaulted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20a%20Spanish%20tourist%20was%20allegedly%20gangraped%20in%20Jharkhand's%20Dumka%2C%20a%20stage%20performer%20has%20accused%20three%20men%20of%20spiking%20her%20drink%20and%20gangraping%20her%20in%20the%20state's%20Palamu%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20arrested%20two%20accused%20and%20one%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2021-year-old%20survivor%20is%20recovering%20at%20a%20government-run%20hospital.%20She%20has%20told%20police%20that%20she%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20had%20come%20to%20Palamu%20to%20perform%20in%20an%20orchestra%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrchestra%20shows%20are%20a%20hugely%20popular%20form%20of%20stage%20entertainment%20in%20small%20Indian%20towns.%20An%20orchestra%20party%20typically%20comprises%20singers%2C%20musicians%20and%20sometimes%2C%20dancers%2C%20who%20perform%20on%20an%20indoor%20or%20outdoor%20stage.%20The%20artistes%20often%20collaborate%20with%20musical%20troupes%20and%20travel%20to%20other%20states%20to%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survivor%20has%20told%20police%20that%20Golu%2C%20one%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20runs%20an%20orchestra%20group%20in%20Palamu.%20He%20had%20called%20her%20and%20her%20sister%20for%20a%20performance%20at%20a%20wedding%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20survivor%20said%20she%20had%20worked%20with%20Golu%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20performance%2C%20she%20said%2C%20was%20cancelled%20and%20Golu%20brought%20them%20to%20his%20home.%20The%20two%20sisters%20were%20given%20separate%20rooms.%20Golu%20then%20offered%20cold%20drinks%20to%20them.%20The%20survivor%20has%20alleged%20that%20her%20drink%20was%20spiked.%20She%20has%20told%20police%20that%20she%20was%20intoxicated%2C%20but%20awake.%20Golu%20and%20two%20others%20repeatedly%20raped%20her%20in%20that%20state%2C%20she%20has%20alleged.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIt%20was%20dawn.%20They%20had%20mixed%20something%20in%20my%20drink%20and%20three%20men%20raped%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20hospital%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palamu%20case%20comes%20days%20after%20Jharkhand%20made%20headlines%20for%20the%20shocking%20violence%20against%20a%20Spanish%20couple%20travelling%20through%20the%20state.%20The%20Spanish%20woman%20has%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20staying%20in%20a%20tent%20when%20some%20men%20assaulted%20her%20husband%20and%20gangraped%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20has%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20at%20least%20seven%20people%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20incident.%20The%20couple%20is%20being%20treated%20at%20a%20local%20hospital%20and%20three%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20said%20the%20incident%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bstain%26quot%3B%20on%20Jharkhand.%20%26quot%3BThis%20shows%20the%20deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20and%20that%20even%20foreigners%20aren't%20safe%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20MLA%20Anant%20Ojha%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20Minister%20Banna%20Gupta%20has%20said%20the%20state%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20taking%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709618580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0htt5beg_india-police-generic_625x300_23_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstage-performer-gangraped-in-jharkhand-days-after-spanish-woman-assaulted-5179191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20a%20Spanish%20tourist%20was%20allegedly%20gangraped%20in%20Jharkhand's%20Dumka%2C%20a%20stage%20performer%20has%20accused%20three%20men%20of%20spiking%20her%20drink%20and%20gangraping%20her%20in%20the%20state's%20Palamu%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstage-performer-gangraped-in-jharkhand-days-after-spanish-woman-assaulted-5179191%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ather%20Energy%20picks%20HSBC%2C%20JPMorgan%2C%20Nomura%2C%20Indian%20banks%20to%20arrange%20its%20IPO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709618565000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F20%2Ffull%2F1700498255-6736.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-energy-picks-hsbc-jpmorgan-nomura-indian-banks-to-arrange-its-ipo-124030500302_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tarun%20Mehta%20and%20Swapnil%20Jain%20founded%20Ather%20in%202013%20after%20graduating%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Madras%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-energy-picks-hsbc-jpmorgan-nomura-indian-banks-to-arrange-its-ipo-124030500302_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-energy-picks-hsbc-jpmorgan-nomura-indian-banks-to-arrange-its-ipo-124030500302_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-energy-picks-hsbc-jpmorgan-nomura-indian-banks-to-arrange-its-ipo-124030500302_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20Bonds%20and%20the%20Curious%20Case%20of%20SBI%20Keeping%20Crucial%20Data%20in%20Physical%20Form%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105750%2F1166496076_ac2efae08c_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20afternoon%20of%20March%204%2C%202024%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20filed%20an%20application%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20requesting%20the%20court%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGrant%20time%20to%20the%20Applicant%20Bank%20until%2030.06.2024%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20directions%20in%20its%20Judgement%20dated%2015.02.2024%20in%20W.P.%20(C)%20No.%20880%20of%202017%20and%20batch.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20judgment%20in%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20the%20SBI%20to%20%E2%80%9Csubmit%20the%20details%20of%20political%20parties%20which%20have%20received%20contributions%20through%20Electoral%20Bonds%E2%80%A6to%20the%20ECI.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20SBI%20must%20disclose%20details%20of%20each%20electoral%20bond%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties%20and%20include%20the%20date%20of%20encashment%20and%20the%20denomination%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond.%20The%20apex%20court%20said%20that%20the%20SBI%20is%20to%20submit%20this%20information%20to%20the%20ECI%20within%20three%20weeks%20from%20the%20date%20of%20this%20judgment%2C%20that%20is%2C%20by%20March%206%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20application%20makes%20some%20startling%20disclosures%2C%20possibly%20inadvertently.%20The%20main%20one%20is%20that%20some%20of%20the%20data%20was%20not%20stored%20digitally.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20the%20application%20speak%20for%20itself%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C10.%20It%20is%20submitted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edonor%20details%20were%20kept%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20designated%20branches%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eall%20such%20sealed%20covers%20were%20deposited%20in%20the%20Main%20Branch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20Applicant%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C11.%20On%20the%20other%20end%2C%20each%20political%20party%20was%20required%20to%20maintain%20a%20designated%20account%20in%20any%20of%20the%2029%20authorised%20Branches.%20It%20was%20only%20in%20this%20account%20that%20electoral%20bonds%20received%20by%20that%20party%20could%20be%20deposited%20and%20redeemed.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20redemption%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20original%20bond%2C%20the%20pay-in%20slip%20would%20be%20stored%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20SBI%20Mumbai%20Main%20Branch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C13.%20It%20is%20submitted%20that%20the%20retrieval%20of%20information%20from%20each%20silo%20and%20the%20procedure%20of%20matching%20the%20information%20of%20one%20silo%20to%20that%20of%20the%20other%20would%20be%20a%20time%20consuming%20exercise.%20The%20details%20are%20stored%20separately%2C%20some%20of%20the%20details%20such%20as%20number%20of%20Bonds%2C%20etc.%20are%20stored%20digitally%20while%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20other%20set%20of%20details%20such%20as%20name%20of%20purchaser%2C%20KYC%20etc.%2C%20are%20stored%20physically%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20purpose%20of%20not%20storing%20all%20details%20digitally%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20gathered%20easily%20to%20achieve%20the%20object%20of%20the%20scheme%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20italics%20were%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3Efirst%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20thing%20that%20astounds%20is%20the%20storage%20of%20data%20in%20%E2%80%9Cphysical%E2%80%9D%20form%2C%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20is%20indeed%20amazing%20that%20the%20SBI%20expects%20anyone%2C%20least%20of%20all%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20been%20working%20very%20diligently%20to%20digitalise%20its%20own%20working%2C%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20largest%20bank%20of%20a%20country%2C%20which%20is%20the%20world%20leader%20in%20UPI%20(Unified%20Payments%20Interface)%2C%20is%20keeping%20such%20critical%20data%20in%20physical%20form.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3Esecond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20what%20the%20application%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20paragraph%2012%20above%2C%20says%20about%20the%20internal%20working%20of%20the%20SBI.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20us%20imagine%20a%20scenario%20that%20(a)%20a%20purchaser%20buys%20an%20electoral%C2%A0%20bond%20worth%20Rs%2010%20crores%20at%20the%20SBI%20Main%20Branch%20at%20Parliament%20Street%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20(b)%20gives%20it%20to%20an%20eligible%20political%20party%20in%20Patna%2C%20(c)%20the%20political%20party%20presents%20this%20electoral%20bond%20for%20redemption%20at%20the%20SBI%20Main%20Branch%20at%20Kolkata%20where%20it%20has%20a%20designated%20account%20for%20this%20purpose%20(which%20it%20is%20legally%2C%20under%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20as%20it%20existed%2C%20permitted%20to%20do)%20within%2015%20days%20of%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20electoral%C2%A0%20bond%20by%20SBI%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20application%2C%20and%20paragraph%2012%20in%20particular%2C%20seem%20to%20indicate%20that%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(a)%20SBI%20New%20Delhi%20will%20send%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdonor%20details%E2%80%9D%20such%20as%20the%20KYC%20particulars%20of%20the%20purchaser%20to%20SBI%20Main%20Branch%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20in%20a%20physical%20form%2C%20without%20keeping%20a%20digital%20record%2C%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(b)%20SBI%20Kolkata%20will%20deposit%20Rs%2010%20crores%20in%20the%20designated%20account%20of%20the%20political%20party%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eapparently%20without%20any%20reference%20to%20or%20verification%20from%20the%20SBI%20New%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20send%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20original%20bond%2C%20the%20pay-in%20slip%E2%80%A6in%20a%20sealed%20cover%E2%80%A6to%20the%20SBI%20Mumbai%20Main%20Branch%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20stated%20in%20paragraph%2011%20of%20the%20application.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20another%20interesting%20facet%20is%20the%20chronology%2C%20though%20it%20is%20very%20short.%20The%20direction%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20was%20given%20to%20the%20SBI%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%2015%2C%20and%20the%20application%20was%20filed%20on%20March%204.%20It%20took%20the%20largest%20bank%20in%20the%20country%2017%20days%2C%20from%20February%2016%20to%20March%2003%2C%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20it%20cannot%20provide%20the%20information%20by%20March%206%20but%20will%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20it%20only%20by%20June%2030!%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEfficiency%2C%20anyone%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20other%20anomalies%20in%20the%20application.%20What%20is%20deeply%20saddening%20is%20how%20predictable%20the%20application%20is.%20The%20SC%20judgment%20was%20delivered%20on%20February%2015%2C%202024.%20Speculation%20appeared%20very%20soon%20thereafter%20that%20ways%20may%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Felectoral-bonds-bank-rules-may-impede-revealing-poll-bond-information-say-government-sources%2Farticleshow%2F107764097.cms%5C%22%3Efound%20to%20impede%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20judgment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20piece%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fcomment%2Fopportunity-to-save-democracy-from-big-money-592142%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan