to%20thousands%20of%20deaths%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20has%20said%20it%20is%20deeply%20troubled%20by%20the%20conflict%20and%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20it%20has%20led%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20briefing%20at%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%2C%20Permanent%20Representative%20of%20India%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20Ruchira%20Kamboj%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20has%20led%20to%20a%20large-scale%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%2C%20especially%20women%20and%20children%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20simply%20unacceptable.%20We%20have%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20deaths%20of%20civilians%20in%20the%20conflict.%20India%20has%20a%20longstanding%20and%20uncompromising%20position%20against%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20committed%20to%20supporting%20a%20two-state%20solution%20where%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20are%20able%20to%20live%20freely%20in%20an%20independent%20country%20within%20secure%20borders%20with%20due%20regard%20to%20the%20security%20needs%20of%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709618040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F6om8qmno_hezbollah_625x300_05_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-hezbollah-2-others-injured-as-hezbollah-strikes-orchard-in-north-israel-5178760%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20first%20Indian%20casualty%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20a%20man%20from%20Kerala%20died%20in%20a%20missile%20strike%20in%20north%20Israel's%20Margaliot%20yesterday.%20The%20Israel%20embassy%20in%20India%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20this%20morning%20that%20two%20others%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bcowardly%26quot%3B%20attack%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-ne