he%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20on%20Tuesday%20removed%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20UP%20Police%20Recruitment%20Board%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chairperson%2C%20Renuka%20Mishra%2C%20has%20been%20replaced%20with%20IPS%20officer%20Rajeev%20Krishna%2C%20days%20after%20the%20UP%C2%A0police%20constable%20recruitment%20examination%20was%20cancelled%20following%20allegations%20of%20a%20question%20paper%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2048%20lakh%20candidates%20appeared%20in%20the%20examination%2C%20which%20was%20held%20on%20February%2017%20and%2018%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20on%20February%2024%20cancelled%20the%20police%20constable%20recruitment%20examination%20and%20said%20a%20re-examination%20would%20be%20conducted%20within%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20said%20that%20a%20Special%20Task%20Force%20(STF)%20would%20probe%20the%20paper%20leak%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20last%20month%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20can%20be%20no%20compromise%20with%20the%20sanctity%20of%20examinations%26quot%3B%20and%20assured%20strict%20action%20against%20%26quot%3Bunruly%20elements%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20compromise%20with%20the%20sanctity%20of%20examinations.%20Those%20who%20toy%20with%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20youngsters%20will%20not%20be%20spared%20under%20any%20circumstances.%20Strictest%20action%20is%20certain%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20such%20unruly%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709617680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fv5k6l3sg_up-police-recruitment-paper-leak_625x300_05_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-police-recruitment-board-chairperson-renuka-mishra-removed-over-paper-leak-51789