mpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finfibeam-avenues-gets-rbi-s-authorisation-for-payment-aggregator-licence-124030500249_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finfibeam-avenues-gets-rbi-s-authorisation-for-payment-aggregator-licence-124030500249_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Is%20Ashwin%20So%20Late%20To%20100%20Tests%3F%20Pujara%20Talks%20About%20'Various%20Reasons'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20sharp%20mind%20with%20a%20penchant%20for%20trying%20out%20new%20things%2C%20senior%20off-spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20relentless%20in%20his%20bowling%20approach%20and%20always%20tries%20to%20keep%20himself%20one%20step%20ahead%20of%20opposition%20batters%2C%20his%20long-time%20national%20team-mate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Cheteshwar%20Pujara%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F897-cheteshwar-pujara-playerprofile%5C%22%3ECheteshwar%20Pujara%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%20Ashwin%20is%20set%20to%20play%20his%20100th%20Test%20in%20the%20last%20game%20of%20the%20five-match%20series%20in%20Dharamsala%20beginning%20on%20March%207.%20He%20went%20past%20the%20500-wicket%20mark%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20in%20Rajkot%20to%20become%20only%20the%20second%20Indian%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReading%20batters%20has%20always%20been%20a%20key%20part%20of%20what%20Ash%20does.%20He%20is%20always%20one%20step%20ahead%2C%20alert%20to%20the%20smallest%20cues.%20He%20is%20constantly%20observing%20the%20batter...%20No%20detail%20is%20too%20small%20for%20his%20sharp%20mind.%20He%20puts%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20into%20each%20delivery%2C%26quot%3B%20Pujara%20wrote%20in%20his%20column%20for%20'ESPNcricinfo'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20just%20become%20the%20second%20quickest%20bowler%20to%20500%20Test%20wickets%2C%20Ash%20now%20deserves%20another%20equally%20significant%20landmark%20-%20of%20100%20Tests.%20He's%20probably%20a%20little%20late%20getting%20there%20for%20various%20reasons.%20But%20I%20am%20really%20happy%20for%20him.%20He%20is%20someone%20who%20has%20always%20been%20ready%20to%20take%20the%20challenge%20on%20and%20do%20the%20hard%20yards%20for%20the%20team.%20He%20deserves%20it%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20evolved%20and%20survived%20for%20a%20long%20time%20despite%20playing%20multiple%20formats%2C%20and%20that%20is%20mainly%20because%20of%20his%20innovative%20mind%3A%20he%20is%20not%20afraid%20or%20shy%20to%20try%20out%20new%20things%2C%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20failing%20in%20the%20process.%26quot%3B%20Pujara%2C%20who%20also%20played%20his%20100th%20Test%20last%20year%20but%20has%20been%20out%20favour%20currently%2C%20said%20there%20was%20no%20respite%20for%20batters%20while%20facing%20Ashwin%20as%20he%20was%20always%20on%20a%20look-out%20for%20taking%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20respite.%20If%20you're%20comfortable%20batting%20against%20him%20from%20over%20the%20stumps%2C%20he%20will%20change%20to%20round%20the%20stumps%2C%20from%20where%20he%20is%20able%20to%20create%20that%20angle%20where%2C%20if%20the%20ball%20goes%20straight%2C%20there's%20an%20edge%20in%20play%20even%20if%20you%20are%20looking%20to%20defend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20constantly%20observing%20the%20batter%2C%20his%20trigger%2C%20where%20the%20backlift%20is%20coming%20from%2C%20which%20stump%20he%20is%20on.%20So%20if%20a%20batter%20is%20looking%20to%20sweep%2C%20Ash%20will%20go%20a%20little%20fuller%20and%20try%20and%20block%20him%20by%20bowling%20the%20quicker%20delivery%2C%20almost%20a%20yorker%20length%2C%20and%20get%20an%20lbw.%26quot%3B%20Pujara%20cited%20an%20example%20of%20Ashwin's%20meticulous%20preparation%20before%20a%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Ashwin)%20has%20spoken%20previously%20about%20how%20he%20obsessively%20pored%20over%20videos%20of%20Steve%20Smith%20several%20months%20before%20India's%20tour%20of%20Australia%20in%202020-21.%20Before%20the%20Melbourne%20Test%2C%20I%20remember%20we%20chalked%20out%20the%20plan%20of%20having%20a%20leg%20gully%20against%20Smith%20because%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20moisture%2C%20which%20made%20the%20ball%20hold%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20Ash%20ended%20up%20bowling%20with%20the%20new%20ball.%20Part%20of%20the%20plan%20was%20also%20that%20he%20would%20come%20round%20the%20stumps%20to%20create%20the%20angle.%20And%20the%20plan%20worked%20-%20I%20caught%20Smith%20at%20leg%20gully.%26quot%3B%20Pujara%20also%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20%26quot%3Benjoying%20up%20close%26quot%3B%20Ashwin's%20duels%20against%20star%20England%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Joe%20Root%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1433-joe-root-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJoe%20Root%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20fine%20player%20of%20spin.%20The%20two%20are%20set%20to%20renew%20their%20rivalry%20in%20Dharamsala%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20his%20record%2C%20Root%20has%20always%20been%20a%20proactive%20batter%20-%20he%20will%20either%20try%20to%20play%20the%20sweep%20or%20reverse%20sweep%2C%20or%20try%20to%20rotate%20the%20strike%20so%20he%20doesn't%20have%20to%20face%20six%20balls%20off%20any%20particular%20bowler.%20I'm%20not%20saying%20that%20Root%20doesn't%20defend%20well%2C%20but%20overall%2C%20his%20game%20plan%20is%20to%20put%20bowlers%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20counter%20that%2C%20Ashwin's%20tactic%20has%20been%20to%20keep%20Root%20on%20strike%20by%20taking%20out%20the%20short%20leg%20or%20other%20close-in%20fielders%2C%20leaving%20just%20one%20slip%2C%20and%20placing%20a%20fielder%20at%20square%20leg%20to%20prevent%20the%20single.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20whether%20you%20are%20playing%20on%20a%20flat%20pitch%20or%20on%20a%20turner%2C%20Ash%20wants%20Root%20to%20defend%20those%20six%20balls%20and%20see%20how%20he%20reacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20battle%20of%20wills%20between%20two%20top%20players%2C%20which%20makes%20for%20an%20engrossing%20contest.%26quot%3B%20Pujara%20also%20described%20Ashwin%20as%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20one%20of%20the%20fittest%20I%20have%20known%26quot%3B%20among%20the%20bowlers%2C%20ending%20up%20bowling%2030%2C%2035%2C%2040%20overs%20in%20a%20day%2C%20but%20he%20still%20has%20the%20stamina%20to%20carry%20on%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20cricket%20matters%2C%20Pujara%20said%20%26quot%3Byou%20can%20never%20win%20an%20argument%26quot%3B%20against%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20very%20smart%2C%20and%20his%20vocabulary%20is%20probably%20among%20the%20best%20in%20the%20cricketing%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20Ash%20is%20not%20a%20bad%20loser.%20We%20play%20table%20tennis%20and%20tennis%20-%20two%20things%20in%20which%20I%20enjoy%20having%20an%20edge%20over%20him!%20-%20and%20he%20is%20a%20good%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20I%20had%20his%20incredible%20memory.%20That%20is%20probably%20because%20he%20has%20a%20mind%20that%20is%20always%20ticking.%20Away%20from%20cricket%2C%20he%20is%20a%20voracious%20reader%2C%20enjoys%20chess%20online%2C%20and%20is%20open%20to%20learning%20new%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709616900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2F2t52but_ashwin-pujara-twitter_625x300_11_June_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-is-r-ashwin-so-late-to-100-tests-cheteshwar-pujara-pujara-talks-about-various-reasons-5175949%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22R%20Ashwin%20is%20set%20to%20play%20his%20100th%20Test%20in%20the%20last%20game%20of%20the%20five-match%20series%20in%20Dharamsala%20beginning%20on%20March%207%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nilgiris%3A%20Water%20Shortage%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Pose%20Threats%20to%20Biodiversity%20and%20Livelihoods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105623%2Farfan-abdulazeez-SH_DiXK60XY-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoonoor%20(Nilgiris)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Vasanthan%20Panchavarnam%20came%20to%20Coonoor%2030%20years%20back%20on%20a%20transfer%20from%20Chennai%20as%20a%20physician.%20The%20hilly%20district%20stole%20his%20heart%20and%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20his%20permanent%20home.%20When%20some%20friends%20who%20he%20hung%20out%20with%20became%20interested%20in%20exploratory%20walks%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20picked%20up%20the%20binoculars%20and%20started%20going%20around.%20The%20change%20we%20have%20observed%20is%20tremendous%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENilgiris%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20northwestern%20part%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnilgiris.nic.in%2Fabout-district%2F%5C%22%3Ebetween%20900-2%2C636%20metres%3C%2Fa%3E%20above%20mean%20sea%20level.%20More%20than%20half%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnilgiris.nic.in%2Fdepartments%2Fdepartment-of-horticulture-and-plantation-crops%2F%5C%22%3E56%25%3C%2Fa%3E)%20of%20its%20total%20area%20is%20under%20natural%20vegetation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty%20years%20back%2C%20when%20Panchavarnam%20relocated%2C%20it%20was%20a%20quiet%20town%20with%20a%20flourishing%20local%20ecology.%20The%20rolling%20grasslands%2C%20dense%20woods%20and%20cool%20climate%20captured%20the%20hearts%20of%20nature%20lovers.%20But%20once%20it%20started%20attracting%20tourists%20and%20businesses%2C%20leading%20to%20landscape%20alteration%20and%20subsequent%20warming%2C%20the%20town%20started%20to%20lose%20its%20biodiverse%20verdancy%2C%20native%20flora%2C%20and%20wildlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETemperatures%20rise%2C%20rainfall%20becomes%20erratic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemperature%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20Nilgiris%20have%20been%20observed%20for%20the%20last%20two%20centuries%20and%20several%20references%20to%20it%20are%20found%20in%20books%20and%20hunters%E2%80%99%20journals%2C%20Panchavarnam%20tells%20us.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Neilgherries%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FNeilgherries-Robert-Baikie%2Fdp%2F1021987697%5C%22%3Etravelogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%201857%20detailing%20the%20travels%20of%20medical%20superintendent%20Robert%20Baikie%20in%20the%20district%2C%20says%20that%20between%201831%20and%201833%2C%20the%20mean%20temperature%20was%2016.8%20degree%20Centigrade%20(now%20Celsius).%20Between%201901-06%2C%20it%20was%2013.8%20degree%20Centigrade%20and%20in%202016%2C%20the%20mean%20was%2024.1%20degree%20Centigrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%222030c22a-9ba9-4406-bcf9-b627de69450e%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Rising%20Annual%20Maximum%20Temperature%20In%20The%20Nilgiris%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%226e651210-aea3-43d0-a267-798c8323d6f1%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Rising%20Annual%20Minimum%20Temperature%20In%20The%20Nilgiris%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20had%20begun%20exploiting%20the%20land%20over%20two%20centuries%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20three%20major%20towns%20in%20the%20geographical%20domain%20from%20Kodanaadu%20to%20Naduvattam%20namely%20Coonoor%2C%20Kotagiri%20and%20Ooty%20were%20exploited%20with%20buildings%20and%20plantations%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Philip%20K.%20Mulley%2C%20a%20septuagenarian%20resident%2C%20pastor%20at%20the%20local%20church%2C%20and%20long-time%20chronicler%20of%20the%20Nilgiris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20five%20decades%2C%20the%20rainfall%20pattern%20has%20been%20changing%20in%20Nilgiris%3B%20there%20have%20been%20short%2C%20intense%20spells%20with%20drop%20in%20average%20rainfall%20in%20particular%20years%2C%20says%20S.%20Vishwanath%2C%20a%20water%20expert%20and%20educator%20based%20in%20Bengaluru.%20As%20per%20the%20department%20of%20Horticulture%20and%20Plantation%20in%20Nilgiris%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnilgiris.nic.in%2Fdepartments%2Fdepartment-of-horticulture-and-plantation-crops%5C%22%3Ethe%20average%20rainfall%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20district%20is%201%2C522.7%20mm%20per%20annum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%223c879821-da88-4288-8d24-a5378457efad%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Rainfall%20Pattern%20In%20The%20Nilgiris%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20aquifers%20are%20not%20recharged%20and%20so%20the%20springs%20do%20not%20flow%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishwanath%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20springs%20do%20not%20flow%2C%20reservoirs%20do%20not%20fill%20up.%20Then%2C%20there%20is%20shortage%20of%20water%20both%20for%20nature%20and%20living%20beings.%20The%20springs%20affect%20the%20wetlands%20and%20bogs%20which%20in%20turn%20impacts%20the%20grasslands%20also.%20Moreover%2C%20with%20the%20recharge%20zones%20being%20altered%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20of%20forest%20fires%20since%20the%20soil%20moisture%20is%20deficient.%20Temperature%20also%20increases%20because%20there%20is%20not%20enough%20humidity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201850%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fmanualofnlagir00grigrich%2Fpage%2Fn5%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3EBritish%20planted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tasmanian%20Blue%20Gum%20(Eucalyptus%20globulus)%20and%20Black%20Wattle%20(Acacia%20Mearnsii)%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20getting%20firewood.%20The%20weed%20species%20Lantana%20Camara%20also%20came%20into%20the%20hills%20at%20the%20time%2C%20as%20part%20of%20ornamental%20plantation.%20These%20invasive%20species%20spread%20across%20the%20pristine%20habitat%20of%20the%20Nilgiris%2C%20altering%20its%20properties%20and%20making%20it%20vulnerable%2C%20says%20Panchavarnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20spoiling%20the%20grazing%20grounds%20and%20teak%20plantations%20in%20Teppakkadu.%20Sandalwood%20also%20encountered%20a%20rare%20disease%20because%20of%20Lantana.%20Wherever%20forest%20cover%20is%20disturbed%2C%20there%20is%20Lantana%20in%20Nilgiris.%20From%20a%20diverse%20ecosystem%2C%20it%20has%20created%20an%20alternate%20one%2C%20with%20structural%2C%20nutritional%20and%20species%20simplification.%20The%20loss%20of%20diversity%20is%20further%20adding%20a%20block%20to%20mitigating%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoss%20of%20native%20species%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scirp.org%2Fjournal%2Fpaperinformation%3Fpaperid%3D24976%5C%22%3EShola%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20name%20used%20across%20South%20India%20to%20refer%20to%20swathes%20of%20montane%20grasslands%20and%20shrublands%20%E2%80%93%20biomes%2C%20as%20per%20World%20Wildlife%20Fund%20classification.%20Shola%20habitats%20in%20the%20marshlands%20of%20Nilgiris%20comprise%20stunted%20evergreen%20trees%20and%20undulating%20meadows.%20These%20have%20moisture%20retention%20properties%20and%20act%20as%20carbon%20sinks.%20When%20it%20rains%2C%20the%20Shola%20grasslands%20absorb%20the%20water%2C%20preventing%20surface%20run-off.%20With%20its%20deep%20roots%20that%20go%20seven%20feet%20under%2C%20it%20retains%20the%20water%20underground.%20The%20Shola%20ecosystem%20supports%20the%20growth%20of%20native%20species%20that%20are%20endemic%20to%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20habitats%20are%20now%20filled%20with%20Eucalyptus%2C%20Acacia%20and%20tea%2C%20as%20also%20Lantana%2C%20none%20of%20which%20have%20soil-binding%20root%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Panchavarnam.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20result%20is%20that%20the%20run-off%20is%20heavier%2C%20and%20the%20resulting%20soil%20erosion%20degrades%20the%20marshlands.%20With%20the%20dams%20taking%20over%20whatever%20is%20left%20of%20the%20marshlands%2C%20the%20drastic%20landscape%20alteration%20and%20the%20increase%20in%20temperature%20have%20led%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20certain%20native%20bird%20species.%20Thousands%20of%20migrant%20bird%20species%20have%20stopped%20coming%20to%20the%20region.%20Woodcock%20or%20game%20bird%20that%20are%20marshlands-dependent%20are%20rare%20now.%20Egyptian%20vultures%20are%20extinct%20from%20the%20upper%20reaches%2C%20as%20is%20the%20Malabar%20civet.%20Recently%2C%20some%20lost%20species%20are%20re-colonising%20because%20of%20forest%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWoodcutters%2C%20foragers%2C%20animal-grazers%2C%20and%20hunters%20add%20to%20the%20damage.%20The%20population%20of%20the%20Nilgiris%20is%20more%20than%20700%2C000%20and%20the%20area%20is%20experiencing%20rapid%20commercialisation.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20wetlands%20are%20replaced%20by%20buildings%20within%20the%20urban%20limits%20of%20Kotagiri%20and%20Coonoor%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mulley%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClimate-change%20impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClimate-change%20impact%20is%20felt%20both%20in%20loss%20of%20livelihoods%20and%20man-animal%20conflict.%20Last%20year%2C%20both%20monsoons%20failed%20and%20the%20district%20received%20heavy%20rainfall%20up%20to%2050%20cm%20overnight.%20This%20resulted%20in%20landslides%3B%20all%20the%20vegetables%20ready%20for%20harvest%20were%20washed%20away%20in%20the%20heavy%20downpour%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Azad%20Kamil%2C%20founder%2C%20Ongil%20Nature%20Trust%2C%20an%20NGO%20in%20Coonoor%20that%20works%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20nature%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.s3waas.gov.in%2Fs339461a19e9eddfb385ea76b26521ea48%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F2018040983.pdf%5C%22%3Enative%20tribes%3C%2Fa%3E%20viz.%20Kurumbars%2C%20Irulars%2C%20Todas%2C%20Paniyars%20and%20Kattunayakars%2C%20many%20locals%20have%20left%20their%20properties%20behind%20and%20migrated%20to%20the%20plains%20in%20search%20of%20reliable%20occupations.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20localities%20like%20Rambla%20that%20are%20dominant%20with%20tea%20estates%2C%20many%20gated%20communities%20have%20mushroomed.%20This%20area%20was%20habituated%20by%20species%20such%20as%20Sambar%20deer%2C%20rabbits%2C%20Leopard%20and%20leopard%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20afforestation%20and%20encroachment%2C%20these%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20habitat%20to%20thrive.%20In%20fact%2C%20large%20carnivores%20are%20lesser%20in%20number%20now%20and%20so%20the%20population%20of%20herbivores%20such%20as%20bison%20and%20bears%20have%20become%20more%20and%20they%20are%20entering%20the%20towns%20and%20turning%20into%20a%20menace%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Panchavarnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%20cobras%20are%20not%20found%20in%20winters.%20But%20two%20Cobras%20were%20rescued%20last%20week%20in%20Kethi.%20Two%20years%20back%2C%20we%20rescued%20a%2013-foot%20King%20Cobra%20in%20Kattery%2C%20located%203%20km%20from%20Coonoor.%20Peacocks%2C%20abundant%20originally%20in%20Mudhumalai%2C%20are%20sighted%20in%20Coonoor.%20The%20most%20important%20is%20mosquitoes%20in%20the%20hills%20during%20winter%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Kamil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUndoing%20the%20damage%20and%20restoring%20balance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20climate%20change%20being%20experienced%20in%20the%20Nilgiris%20is%20anthropogenic.%20Lantana%2C%20that%20is%20present%20everywhere%20except%20the%20upper%20reaches%2C%20cannot%20be%20removed%20totally%2C%20says%20Panchavarnam%2C%20because%20if%20even%20a%20small%20root%20is%20left%2C%20it%20grows%20and%20spreads%20rapidly.%20Also%2C%20because%20of%20the%20inedible%20nature%20of%20its%20leaves%2C%20herbivores%20cannot%20consume%20it.%20But%20the%20berries%20are%20edible%20and%20so%20the%20seeds%20get%20dispersed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20conserve%20the%20remaining%20ecosystem%20and%20prevent%20soil%20erosion%20and%20water%20shortages%2C%20says%20Vishwanath%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20focus%20on%20spring%20protection%20and%20rejuvenation%20and%20identifying%20and%20conserving%20natural%20recharge%20zones%20is%20essential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Forest%20Department%20conducted%20a%20campaign%20to%20remove%20many%20exotic%20species%20in%20the%20Nilgiris%20biosphere%20reserve%2C%20such%20as%20Acacia%20mearnsii%2C%20and%20the%20native%20sholas%20planted%20in%20the%20region%20have%20started%20to%20reoccupy%20the%20canopy%20gaps%2C%20said%20Rekha%20R.%20Warrier%2C%20a%20scientist%20at%20the%20Institute%20of%20Forest%20Genetics%20and%20Tree%20Breeding%20(IFGTB)%2C%20Coimbatore.%20Being%20unique%2C%20the%20sholas%20require%20a%20long-term%20perspective%20and%20a%20socioecological%20landscape%20management%20process%20implemented%20in%20a%20participatory%20manner%20with%20Indigenous%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20communities%20interested%20in%20protecting%20their%20traditional%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fao.org%2Fdocuments%2Fcard%2Fen%2Fc%2Fcc8955en%5C%22%3Ecase%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20conducted%20and%20reported%20as%20part%20of%20a%20working%20paper%20on%20forest%20and%20Landscape%20Restoration%20supported%20by%20the%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organization%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20three%20selected%20shola%20pockets%20in%20Nilgiris%20suggest%20that%20these%20open%20patches%20should%20be%20fenced%2C%20and%20that%20native%20species%20should%20be%20reintroduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSpecies%20able%20to%20establish%20in%20open%20landscapes%2C%20such%20as%20Syzygium%20cumini%2C%20can%20be%20beneficial%20in%20restoration%20initiatives.%20Of%20course%2C%20projected%20changes%20in%20rainfall%20patterns%20and%20temperature%20could%20endanger%20intolerant%20endemic%20species%2C%20due%20to%20their%20narrow%20genetic%20base%20and%20restoration%20of%20species%20with%20small%20population%20sizes%20is%20a%20challenge%2C%20and%20introduction%20from%20adjacent%20forest%20patches%20would%20be%20necessary%20to%20increase%20their%20genetic%20diversity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic-led%20conservation%20efforts%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20district%20collector%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20are%20aimed%20at%20replanting%20Shola%20grass%20and%20remapping%20water%20resources%20to%20prevent%20further%20degradation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administrators%20need%20to%20bring%20strict%20rules%20and%20follow%20them%20diligently%2C%20feel%20residents.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Nilgiris%20biosphere%20zone%20should%20be%20considered%20in%20isolation%20%E2%80%93%20the%20general%20conservation%20rules%20made%20for%20the%20state%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20applicable%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mulley%20voices%20the%20collective%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDeveloping%20a%20carrying%20capacity%20and%20environmental%20management%20plan%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20relooking%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2Fen%2Flibrary%2Fresource%2Freport-of-the-western-ghats-ecology-expert-panel%2F%5C%22%3EGadgil%20Committee%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20and%20implementing%20its%20recommendations%2C%E2%80%9D%20concludes%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fearthcheckindia%2Fnilgiris-reel-under-water-shortage-climate-change-897217%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20IndiaSpend.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709616787000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105623%2Farfan-abdulazeez-SH_DiXK60XY-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fnilgiris-water-shortage-and-climate-change-pose-threats-to-biodiversity-and-livelihoods%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Nilgiris%20has%20been%20warming%20since%20the%201800s%2C%20travelogues%20and%20journal%20entries%20from%20the%20period%20reveal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fnilgiris-water-shortage-and-climate-change-pose-threats-to-biodiversity-and-livelihoods%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shark%20Tank%20Participant%20Slams%20Vineeta%20Singh%3A%20%26quot%3BWas%20Trying%20To%20Hold%20Back%20Tears%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203%20participant%20and%20House%20of%20Beauty%20Founder%20Vibhuti%20Arora%20recently%20discussed%20her%20time%20on%20the%20show.%20Ms%20Arora%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20face%20yoga%20expert%2C%20was%20not%20able%20to%20secure%20any%20investment%20in%20the%20show.%20She%20criticised%20the%20'sharks'%20and%20said%20that%20she%20was%20trying%20to%20hold%20back%20tears%20during%20her%20pitch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Arora%20was%20speaking%20to%20Ayushman%20Pandita%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWi0bW8jjack%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20shown%20was%20still%20very%20nice%2C%20what%20actually%20happened%20was%20a%20lot%20worse.%20I%20could%20feel%20angst%2C%20Vineeta%20kept%20repeating%20the%20same%20thing%2010%20times%2C%20and%20she%20kept%20criticising%20my%20packaging%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20let%20me%20speak.%20I%20was%20there%20to%20get%20their%20help%2C%20as%20a%20bootstrapped%20entrepreneur.%20If%20I%20had%20had%20everything%20sorted%20already%2C%20why%20would%20I%20go%20to%20them%20for%20help%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20stated%20that%20she%20just%20wanted%20%26quot%3Bto%20run%20away%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20show.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20control%20myself%20from%20crying%20after%20one%20point.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20run%20away%20from%20Shark%20Tank.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20cry%20on%20national%20television.%20Vineeta%20kept%20asking%20me%20what%20the%20differentiator%20in%20my%20products%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20podcast%20host.%20Ms%20Arora%20even%20said%20that%20she%20would%20like%20to%20ask%20the%20Sugar%20Cosmetics%20CEO%20about%20the%20differentiator%20in%20lipstick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20calm%20on%20the%20show.%20I%20was%20so%20scared.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20in%20a%20cage%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Vibhuti%20Arora%20said%20about%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%20%C2%A0She%20stated%20that%20she%20suffered%20a%20blackout%20after%20the%20shoot.%20%26quot%3BInitially%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20manage%20to%20get%20funding%20from%20there.%20But%20later%2C%20I%20figured%20that%20I%20was%20not%20going%20to%20get%20anything%20out%20of%20this%2C%20I%20only%20had%20to%20keep%20defending%20myself.%20After%20the%20pitch%2C%20I%20had%20a%20blackout.%20I%20got%20anxious%20that%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Arora%20added%20that%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Emcure%20Pharmaceuticals%20Namita%20Thapar%20was%20her%20%26quot%3Bdream%20shark%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20work%20with%20her%2C%20Peyush%20Bansal%2C%20and%20Azhar%20Iqubal.%20Azhar%20is%20very%20humble%20and%20genuine%2C%20his%20approach%20can%20help%20a%20brand%20like%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20her%20sales%20have%20improved%20from%20Rs%2045%20lakh%20in%20January%20this%20year%20to%20nearly%20Rs%201%20crore%20after%20the%20airing%20of%20the%20episode.%20%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20has%20come%20in%20the%20product%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20video%20has%20amassed%20several%20reactions%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20absolutely%20right%20and%20as%20an%20audience%20I%20did%20watch%20that%20episode%20and%20it%20was%20very%20clear%20that%20vineeta%20was%20getting%20jealous%20of%20her%20.%20I%20did%20also%20comment%20briefly%20in%20that%20episode%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%20sharks%20had%20a%20valid%20point....why%20aren't%20the%20ingredients%20mentioned%20above%2010ml%20bottle.....if%20you%20are%20so%20clean%20jn%20terms%20of%20your%20products%20you%20should%20flaunt%20it%20in%20the%20bottle%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20the%20product%20but%20also%20I%20guess%20Vineeta%20and%20Namita%20handled%20really%20well%20and%20gave%20nice%20feedback%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20seeing%20the%20pitch%20of%20her%20brand%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20she%20is%20trying%20to%20boast%20and%20be%20defensive%20about%20her%20brand.%20Because%20she%20haven't%20got%20a%20deal%20there%2C%20now%20she%20is%20trying%20to%20gain%20sympathy.%20Think%20about%20the%20pitch%20of%20glass%20ka%20mask%20and%20fruit%20ripening%20detector%2C%20Bummer%20where%20ashneer%20heavily%20roasted%20these%20brands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709616720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3ua2kj6_shark-tank_625x300_05_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fshark-tank-india-participant-slams-vineeta-singh-says-was-trying-to-hold-back-tears-5179037%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20