%5C%22%3Efor%20a%20second%20term%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20last%20month's%20elections%2C%20independent%20candidates%20backed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fillegal-shehbaz-sharifs-rival-contender-as-former-picked-for-top-post-5169641%5C%22%3EImran%20Khan's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20ended%20up%20winning%2093%20National%20Assembly%20seats%2C%20defying%20all%20odds%20and%20the%20military's%20will.%20But%20it%20could%20not%20win%20enough%20seats%20to%20form%20a%20majority%20government%20on%20its%20own.%20The%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20of%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20came%20in%20second%20with%2075%20seats%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20People's%20Party%20(PPP)%20of%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20with%2054%20seats.%20This%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshehbaz-sharif-becomes-pakistan-prime-minister-for-second-term-after-winning-crucial-vote-5167747%5C%22%3Esome%20kind%20of%20coalition%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20veritable%20necessity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20weeks%20of%20political%20negotiations%20and%20horse-trading%2C%20an%20eight-party%20coalition%20was%20formed%2C%20which%20has%20now%20assumed%20power%20with%20Sharif%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3B%20PPP%20co-chair%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20would%20be%20the%20new%20president.%20The%20dissonance%20in%20Pakistani%20polity%20was%20evident%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-shehbaz-sharif-faces-a-tougher-task-in-2nd-term-as-pak-pm-5171429%5C%22%3EShehbaz%20Sharif%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20speech%20thanked%20his%20older%20brother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnot-wrong-to-say-nawaz-sharif-is-the-one-who-built-pak-shehbaz-sharif-5168411%5C%22%3ENawaz%2C%20describing%20him%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20one%20who%20built%20Pakistan%E2%80%9D%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20Imran%20Khan's%20supporters%20called%20the%20new%20alliance%20government%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccoalition%20of%20losers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisenchantment%20Simmering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20PTI-backed%20candidates%20in%20recent%20elections%20and%20the%20inability%20of%20the%20military%20to%20manage%20the%20selection%20process%20in%20ways%20it%20would%20have%20preferred%20has%20already%20cast%20a%20spell%20over%20the%20future%20stability%20of%20the%20ruling%20coalition.%20People%20defied%20the%20military%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20Sharif-Bhutto%20duopoly%2C%20and%20the%20vote%20was%20so%20strong%20that%20despite%20widespread%20rigging%20and%20several%20seats%20reportedly%20being%20siphoned%20off%20to%20PML-N%20and%20other%20parties%2C%20PTI-backed%20candidates%20managed%20to%20win%20more%20seats%20than%20either%20of%20the%20two%20established%20parties.%20Yet%2C%20the%20two%20dynasties%20are%20now%20back%20in%20power%20and%20the%20disenchantment%20continues%20to%20simmer%20below%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20ensuring%20that%20Imran%20Khan%20could%20not%20be%20kept%20away%20from%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20his%20supporters%20are%20unlikely%20to%20give%20in.%20They%20have%20tasted%20blood%20against%20the%20all-powerful%20Pakistani%20military%20establishment.%20Khan's%20popularity%20remains%20very%20high.%20Despite%20being%20in%20power%20till%202022%20and%20providing%20shambolic%20governance%2C%20Khan%20has%20managed%20to%20preserve%20his%20identity%20as%20an%20outsider%20to%20the%20system%2C%20thereby%20proving%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20challenger%20to%20both%20the%20military%20and%20established%20political%20parties.%20The%20military's%20crackdown%20on%20him%20and%20his%20supporters%20made%20him%20even%20more%20popular%20as%20he%20gained%20sympathy%20for%20being%20the%20target%20of%20an%20establishment%20hell-bent%20on%20keeping%20him%20out%20of%20the%20political%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKhan%20Continues%20To%20Be%20Popular%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%20an%20unstable%20coalition%20in%20power%2C%20Khan%20will%20continue%20to%20wield%20influence%20from%20behind%20the%20bars%2C%20seeking%20to%20disrupt%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20government%20with%20a%20sizeable%20number%20in%20Parliament.%20By%20sitting%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20he%20is%20also%20ensuring%20that%20he%20is%20seen%20as%20not%20compromising%20on%20his%20anti-corruption%20plank.%20The%20coalition%20has%20no%20one%20who%20can%20match%20his%20charisma%20or%20his%20credibility.%20That%20the%20PPP%20decided%20not%20to%20join%20the%20government%20suggests%20that%20it%20is%20already%20concerned%20about%20its%20future%20by%20being%20associated%20with%20a%20seemingly%20discredited%20coalition.%20It%20is%20therefore%20trying%20to%20maintain%20its%20distance%2C%20though%20it%20is%20far%20from%20evident%20whether%20there%20are%20any%20takers%20for%20this%20in%20Pakistan%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20country%20that%20is%20reeling%20under%20multiple%20crises%2C%20this%20is%20the%20worst%20possible%20outcome.%20The%20kind%20of%20policy%20reforms%20that%20are%20needed%20to%20manage%20the%20gargantuan%20challenges%20the%20nation%20faces%20stand%20in%20direct%20contrast%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20government%20that%20is%20being%20formed.%20A%20ragtag%20bunch%20of%20discredited%20parties%20are%20no%20match%20for%20the%20difficulties%20Pakistan%20is%20facing%20on%20every%20front.%20The%20economic%20situation%20is%20particularly%20dire%2C%20with%20inflation%20sky-high%20and%20state%20bankruptcy%20on%20the%20cards.%20For%20foreign%20lenders%2C%20some%20semblance%20of%20political%20stability%20is%20a%20basic%20necessity%20for%20moving%20forward%20with%20financial%20support.%20The%20PML-N-led%20coalition%2C%20which%20few%20expect%20to%20last%20long%2C%20is%20hardly%20likely%20to%20inspire%20any%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Chaos%20Will%20Get%20Worse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20the%20domestic%20challenge%20that%20is%20the%20biggest%20one.%20Political%20polarisation%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20and%20the%20military%20is%20facing%20a%20challenge%20unlike%20any%20in%20recent%20times.%20Khan%20and%20his%20supporters%2C%20buoyed%20by%20their%20remarkable%20electoral%20performance%2C%20will%20ensure%20that%20any%20meaningful%20governance%20is%20almost%20impossible%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20some%20kind%20of%20political%20reconciliation%E2%80%94which%20seems%20unlikely%20any%20time%20soon%20given%20how%20the%20military%20went%20all%20out%20to%20end%20Khan's%20political%20career%2C%20and%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20have%20formed%20the%20new%20government%20in%20Pakistan%20do%20not%20seem%20enthused%20by%20the%20prospect%20of%20running%20the%20country%2C%20but%20those%20who%20are%20outside%20in%20the%20opposition%20are%20basking%20in%20the%20glow%20of%20a%20mandate%20that%20came%20their%20way%20despite%20all%20the%20tactics%20of%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20what%20makes%20Pakistan's%20immediate%20future%20fascinating%20as%20well%20as%20troubled.%20For%20those%20in%20India%20who%20were%20looking%20forward%20to%20some%20kind%20of%20India-Pakistan%20rapprochement%20post-elections%2C%20a%20word%20of%20caution%3A%20the%20chaos%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20worse%20before%20it%20gets%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20books%20include%20'India%20and%20the%20Gulf%3A%20Theoretical%20Perspectives%20and%20Policy%20Shifts'%20(Cambridge%20University%20Press)%20and%20'Politics%20and%20Geopolitics%3A%20Decoding%20India's%20Neighbourhood%20Challenge'%20(Rupa)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709615580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F92iu6qp8_shehbaz-sharif_625x300_24_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharifs-coalition-is-already-on-a-rocky-road-thanks-to-imran-5178943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20eight-party%20coalition%20with%20Sharif%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20inspires%20little%20confidence%20that%20it%20can%20last%20long.%20Among%20its%20biggest%20challenges%20will%20be%20an%20ever-emboldened%20Imran%20Khan%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharifs-coalition-is-already-on-a-rocky-road-thanks-to-imran-5178943%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharifs-coalition-is-already-on-a-rocky-road-thanks-to-imran-5178943%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharifs-coalition-is-already-on-a-rocky-road-thanks-to-imran-5178943%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Philippine%20and%20Chinese%20boats%20collide%20in%20South%20China%20Sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709615515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FCD0D%2Fproduction%2F_132839425_p0hgn2lk.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68476384%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Philippines%20says%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%20manoeuvres%E2%80%9D%20by%20China%20caused%20a%20collision%20in%20the%20disputed%20waters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-asia-68476384%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Emerges%20as%20Second%20Largest%20Beef%20Exporter%20in%20the%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fbeef-2063437_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20by%20the%20environmental%20and%20human%20rights%20group%20Global%20Witness%2C%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68272643%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20revealed%20that%20three%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20major%20meat%20producers%20are%20linked%20to%20acts%20of%20illegal%20deforestation%20in%20the%20Cerrado%20plains%20of%20Brazil.%20The%20investigation%20names%20JBS%2C%20Minerva%20and%20Marfrig%20for%20illegal%20deforestation%2C%20all%20of%20which%20deny%20wrongdoing.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalwitness.org%2Fen%2Fcampaigns%2Fforests%2Fthe-cerrado-crisis-brazils-deforestation-frontline%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20focused%20on%20the%20state%20of%20Mato%20Grosso%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20just%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20expansive%20Cerrado.%20It%20found%20that%20much%20of%20the%20land%20that%20had%20been%20deforested%20for%20ranches%20owned%20by%20the%20three%20companies%20did%20not%20have%20permits%20to%20remove%20the%20trees%2C%20suggesting%20it%20was%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20comes%20as%20the%20deadline%20for%20companies%20to%20comply%20with%20a%20new%20law%20in%20the%20European%20Union%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreen-business.ec.europa.eu%2Fdeforestation-regulation-implementation_en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEU%20Deforestation%20Regulation%3C%2Fa%3E%20draws%20near%20(December%2030%2C%202024%20and%20June%2030%2C%202025%20for%20micro%20or%20small%20businesses).%20According%20to%20the%20EUDR%2C%20all%20companies%20that%20sell%20goods%20to%20the%20EU%20will%20need%20to%20prove%20that%20their%20produce%20was%20not%20grown%20on%20land%20deforested%20after%202020%2C%20or%20else%20face%20heavy%20fines.%20Observers%20say%20that%20this%20law%20will%20penalise%20smallholder%20farmers%20unable%20to%20provide%20the%20relevant%20data%20needed%20to%20comply%2C%20cutting%20off%20important%20streams%20of%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20some%20of%20the%20products%20affected%20by%20this%20law%20will%20be%20beef%2C%20coffee%2C%20palm%20oil%20and%20soy.%20Global%20Witness%20campaigners%20take%20another%20issue%20with%20the%20law%2C%20however%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20not%20stringent%20enough%2C%20as%20its%20current%20wording%20means%20that%20unlike%20the%20Amazon%2C%20the%20Cerrado%20plains%20are%20not%20fully%20covered%20by%20the%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20following%20chart%20shows%2C%20Brazil%20was%20the%20biggest%20exporter%20of%20beef%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdownloads.usda.library.cornell.edu%2Fusda-esmis%2Ffiles%2F73666448x%2Fcn69nh059%2Fzs25zp436%2Flivestock_poultry.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Agriculture.%20Forecasts%2C%20as%20of%20April%202023%2C%20predicted%20that%20the%20country%20would%20export%20more%20than%203%20million%20tons%20of%20beef%20that%20year.%20The%20other%20major%20players%20in%20beef%20exports%20in%202023%20were%20India%2C%20which%20exports%20water%20buffalo%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Australia.%20When%20looking%20at%20the%20countries%20that%20produce%20the%20most%20beef%2C%20a%20different%20order%20appears.%20Then%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F263990%2Fleading-beef-producers-around-the-world-since-2007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20is%20in%20first%20rank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20it%20sells%20much%20of%20its%20beef%20domestically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Infographic%3A%20The%20Biggest%20Exporters%20of%