shankar%2C%20who%20advised%20Europeans%20to%20look%20at%20themselves%20before%20lecturing%20others%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%97%AF%20%26quot%3BMy%20friend%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%20Subramanyam%20Jaishankar%2C%20was%20once%20at%20the%20UN%2C%20giving%20a%20speech.%20He%20was%20asked%20why%20they%20started%20buying%20so%20much%20oil%20from%20Russia.%20He%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FnD4C0YHMDj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FnD4C0YHMDj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sputnik%20India%20(%40Sputnik_India)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSputnik_India%2Fstatus%2F1764634546249617678%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20Russian%20news%20agency%20Sputnik%2C%20the%20country's%20foreign%20affairs%20minister%20Sergey%20Lavrov%20is%20seen%20addressing%20the%20World%20Youth%20Forum%20in%20Sochi.%20%26quot%3BMy%20friend%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%20Subramanyam%20Jaishankar%2C%20was%20once%20at%20the%20UN%2C%20giving%20a%20speech.%20He%20was%20asked%20why%20they%20started%20buying%20so%20much%20oil%20from%20Russia.%20He%20advised%20them%20to%20mind%20their%20own%20business%20and%20reminded%20them%20at%20the%20same%20time%20how%20much%20oil%20the%20West%20had%20started%20buying%20and%20continued%20to%20buy%20oil%20from%20the%20Russian%20Federation.%20This%20is%20national%20dignity%2C%26quot%3B%20Lavrov%20says%20in%20Russian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20broke%20out%2C%20most%20countries%20of%20the%20West%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20Moscow%20and%20stopped%20buying%20crude%20Russian%20oil.%20India%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20to%20play%20along.%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20articulated%20New%20Delhi's%20position%20on%20international%20forums%2C%20emphasising%20that%20Indian%20citizens%20cannot%20afford%20high%20energy%20prices%20and%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20only%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20best%20deal%20possible%20for%20its