ing%20TV%3F%20Especially%20the%20most%20popular%20one%3F%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBecause%20regular%20TV%20can%20give%20you%20that%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20lots%20of%20other%20channels%20that%20won't%20be%20in%20this%20bundle%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20question%20that's%20befuddled%20me%20since%20this%20thing%20was%20announced.%20And%20when%20I%20talk%20to%20people%20in%20the%20industry%20about%20it%2C%20they're%20baffled%2C%20too.%20They're%20constantly%20offering%20up%20alternate%20theories%20about%20why%20this%20thing%20was%20put%20together%2C%20but%20none%20of%20them%20address%20the%20%26quot%3BSeriously%2C%20who's%20going%20to%20buy%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurdoch%20tried%20answering%20that%20Monday%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20tough%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Murdoch%20has%20to%20do%20two%20things%3A%20He%20needs%20to%20convince%20himself%20and%20his%20investors%20that%20there's%20a%20large%20group%20of%20people%20who%20used%20to%20have%20pay%20TV%20but%20cut%20the%20cord%2C%20or%20never%20got%20pay%20TV%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20and%20would%20be%20interested%20in%20paying%20for%20this.%20And%20he%20also%20has%20to%20convince%20that%20same%20audience%20that%20this%20service%20%3Cem%3Ewon't%3C%2Fem%3E%20appeal%20to%20people%20who%20are%20already%20paying%20for%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20that%20it%20won't%20cannibalize%20his%20existing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20answer%2C%20boiled%20down%3A%20Media%20consumers%20and%20analysts%20and%20investors%20who%20live%20on%20the%20coasts%20don't%20get%20it%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20living%20in%20middle%20America%20who%20would%20like%20to%20pay%20for%20sports%20on%20TV.%20They%20just%20don't%20want%20to%20spend%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHuge%20number%20of%20households%20are%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoutside%20of%20the%20bundle%20%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20by%20which%20he%20means%20people%20who%20don't%20get%20the%20traditional%20pay%20TV%20packages%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bfor%20reasons%20other%20than%20that%20they%20don't%20love%20sports%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20outside%20of%20the%20bundle%20that%20are%20still%20very%20strong%2C%20very%20passionate%20sports%20fans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20yes%3A%20Spending%20%2450%20a%20month%20on%20something%20instead%20of%20%2473%20a%20month%20on%20something%20is%20meaningfully%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20can%20also%20flip%20it%20around%3A%20The%20consumers%20Murdoch%20says%20he'll%20reach%20are%20theoretically%20not%20paying%20for%20TV%20at%20all%20right%20now.%20Now%20he's%20asking%20them%20to%20pay%20an%20extra%20%2450%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20get%20everything%20they%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETough%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-streamer-new-nfl-games-who-will-subscribe-lachlan-murdoch-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709589279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e63d31ce7f1785b2e62570%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-streamer-new-nfl-games-who-will-subscribe-lachlan-murdoch-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you're%20a%20big%20enough%20sports%20fan%20that%20you%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20streaming%20TV%2C%20don't%20you%20also%20want%20all%20of%20the%20sports%20on%20streaming%20TV%2C%20especially%20the%20NFL%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A103%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-streamer-new-nfl-games-who-will-subscribe-lachlan-murdoch-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Denis%20Villeneuve%20Cut%20Two%20Actors%20From%20%E2%80%98Dune%202%E2%80%99%20and%20One%20of%20Them%20Is%20%E2%80%98Hear