n-found-criminally-liable-in-manhattan-tax-fraud-trial-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20Manhattan%20jury%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hear%20Weisselberg%20testify%20did%20not%20believe%20him.%20(In%20finding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-organization-found-criminally-liable-in-manhattan-tax-fraud-trial-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20Org%20guilty%20of%20dodging%20payroll%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20rejected%20the%20ex-CFO's%20claim%20that%20in%20running%20the%20scheme%2C%20he'd%20had%20purely%20selfish%20motives%20and%20that%20those%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20ladder%20%E2%80%94%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20two%20eldest%20sons%20%E2%80%94%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeisselberg%20could%20have%20been%20a%20key%20prosecution%20witness%20again%20later%20this%20month%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-organization-found-criminally-liable-in-manhattan-tax-fraud-trial-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20in%20Trump's%20upcoming%20hush%20money%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20Manhattan%20criminal%20trial%20at%20which%20Trump%20faces%20anywhere%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-risks-zero-to-4-years-jail-ny-hush-money-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero%20to%20four%20years%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20prison%20for%20allegedly%20lying%20in%20business%20documents%20to%20hide%20a%20%24130%2C000%20hush-money%20payment%20to%20porn%20actress%20Stormy%20Daniels%20made%20days%20before%20the%202020%20election.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Monday's%20perjury%20plea%20does%20not%20require%20Weisselberg%20to%20cooperate%20in%20any%20way%20with%20prosecutors.%20Instead%2C%20Weisselberg's%20only%20obligation%20between%20now%20and%20his%20April%2010%20sentencing%20is%20to%20remain%20law-abiding%20and%20not%20flee%20the%20jurisdiction%2C%20or%20else%20he'll%20face%20up%20to%20seven%20ye