ligned%20by%20Imran%20Khan%20as%20%E2%80%9Cliberal%20scum%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbloody%20liberals%E2%80%9D%2C%20have%20nevertheless%20been%20fair-minded%20and%20have%20rightly%20criticised%20the%20Feb%208%20elections%20as%20heavily%20managed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20chorus%20alleging%20unfair%20exclusion%20of%20Khan%20and%20his%20PTI.%20True%20enough%2C%20but%20so%20what%3F%20Wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20heavy%20management%20equally%20evident%20in%20the%202018%20elections%20when%20Khan%20rode%20to%20power%20on%20the%20coattails%20of%20those%20who%20later%20dumped%20him%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20two%20wrongs%20cannot%20make%20a%20right.%20However%2C%20thoughtful%20people%20should%20be%20troubled%20by%20much%20else%2C%20not%20just%20the%20travails%20of%20some%20politician%20or%20his%20party.%20Most%20particularly%2C%20they%20should%20be%20appalled%20that%2C%20instead%20of%20strengthening%20democracy%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1812974%5C%22%3EFeb%208%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20simply%20a%20power%20grab%20and%20a%20horse%20race%20followed%20by%20horse%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20candidates%20appeared%20on%20TV%20their%20language%20was%20crude%2C%20aggressive%2C%20and%20ad%20hominem.%20None%20spoke%20of%20plans%20for%20improving%20their%20community%20or%20country%20%E2%80%93%20and%20means%20of%20implementation.%20Past%20experience%20shows%20that%20many%20who%20become%20parliamentarians%20seek%20only%20to%20exponentially%20increase%20their%20wealth%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20election%20run-up%2C%20the%20PML-N%2C%20PTI%2C%20PPP%20and%20other%20rivals%20behaved%20as%20wolf%20packs%2C%20not%20political%20parties.%20Lacking%20defined%20agendas%2C%20they%20reluctantly%20trotted%20out%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1809600%5C%22%3Ehalf-baked%20election%20manifestos%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0hurriedly%20slapped%20together%20just%20days%20earlier.%20Without%20details%20or%20implementation%20schemes%2C%20these%20manifestos%20are%20worthless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1809269%5C%22%3EPersonality%20contests%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sectarian%20and%20tribal%20affiliations%2C%20and%20bribes%20were%20all%20that%20mattered.%20No%20party%20offered%20insight%20into%20preventing%20the%20impending%20apocalypse%20of%20an%20imploding%20economy%2C%20exploding%20population%2C%20and%20resentments%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20Gilgit-Baltistan.%20How%20is%20one%20to%20deal%20with%20desperate%20youth%20with%20university%20degrees%20but%20no%20skills%3F%20Seething%20religious%20fanaticism%20intertwined%20with%20misogyny%3F%20Disappearing%20trust%20in%20key%20institutions%20including%20the%20judiciary%2C%20bureaucracy%2C%20police%20and%20army%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInadvertently%20Feb%208%20transformed%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20jailed%20leader%20into%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20most%20popular%20politician.%20The%20iddat%20case%3A%20what%20a%20joke!%20Such%20clumsy%20persecution%20tactics%20earned%20Khan%20widespread%20sympathy.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20establishment%20worked%20hard%20to%20make%20him%20a%20hero%3B%20this%20time%20it%20did%20that%20by%20vilifying%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%3A%20we%20have%20recently%20seen%20convicted%20felons%20and%20politicians%20whitewashed%20and%20cleared.%20Given%20this%20precedent%20one%20knows%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20release%20will%20come%20within%20months%20or%20years.%20He%20will%20be%20declared%20innocent%20of%20crimes%20that%20he%20did%20not%20commit%20but%20also%20of%20those%20that%20he%20did.%20When%20he%20claws%20his%20way%20back%20to%20the%20top%2C%20a%20dark%20age%20will%20descend%20on%20Pakistan.%20Several%20signs%20point%20to%20this%20dismal%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20recall%20the%20reign%20of%20Emperor%20Khan%20from%20August%202018%20to%20April%202022.%20Surrounded%20by%20bootlickers%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20whom%20deserted%20him%20after%20May%209%2C%202023%20%E2%80%93%20Khan%20filled%20key%20positions%20with%20sycophants.%20This%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1757516%5C%22%3Eappointing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20nincompoop%20as%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%2C%20making%20a%20rank%20opportunist%20his%20closest%20confidante%2C%20choosing%20a%20crony%20general%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1488568%5C%22%3Ehead%20the%20ISI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1615074%5C%22%3Edismissing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20HEC%20chairman%20on%20flimsy%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Khan%20ruled%2C%20religiously%20inspired%20terrorists%20felt%20strongly%20emboldened.%20Accommodating%20TTP%20fighters%20who%20had%20fled%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20he%20invited%20them%20back%20to%20resettle%20in%20North%20Waziristan.%20A%20decade%20earlier%2C%20directly%20after%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1044846%5C%22%3E2013%20suicide%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20All%20Saints%20Church%20in%20Peshawar%2C%20he%20had%20requested%20TTP%20to%20open%20offices%20inside%20Pakistan%20for%20holding%20peace%20talks.%20A%20year%20later%20TTP%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1726659%5C%22%3Emassacred%20141%20children%20and%20teachers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0inside%20the%20Army%20Public%20School%20in%20Peshawar.%20Khan%20was%20booed%20by%20grieving%20parents%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1446168%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98U-turn%20Khan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20earned%20his%20unflattering%20nickname%20after%20breaking%20approximately%20130%20promises%20in%20less%20than%20four%20years.%20As%20just%20one%20example%2C%20weeks%20after%20publicly%20declaring%20Pakistan%20would%20never%20seek%20an%20IMF%20loan%2C%20Khan%20sent%20his%20financial%20managers%20to%20Washington%20to%20ask%20for%20one.%20When%20reminded%20he%20blustered%20that%20reneging%20on%20earlier%20promises%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Challmark%20of%20great%20leadership%E2%80%9D.%20For%20those%20who%20follow%20a%20Pied%20Piper%20through%20narrow%20twisted%20streets%20this%20may%20not%20matter%20but%20people%20who%20value%20consistency%20and%20truth%20were%20unconvinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20saw%20an%20attempt%20at%20further%20tightening%20of%20the%20draconian%20Peca%20law%20(now%20being%20used%20to%20suppress%20PTI%20itself)%2C%20a%20decrease%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20ranking%20on%20the%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Index%2C%20and%20a%20worsening%20of%20Pakis%C2%ADtan%E2%80%99s%20ranking%20on%20Transparency%20International%E2%80%99s%20corruption%20perception%20index.%20As%20the%20Toshakhana%20and%20Al%20Qadir%20cases%20show%2C%20Mr%20Clean%20was%20no%20cleaner%20than%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Echor%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0politicians%20he%20viciously%20attacked%20for%20having%20pocketed%20public%20monies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20negative%20impact%20of%20the%20SNC%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1572130%5C%22%3ESingle%20National%20Curriculum%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20possibly%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20disservice%20to%20Pakistan.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20public%20and%20private%20schools%20%E2%80%93%20all%20except%20those%20for%20the%20super-elite%20%E2%80%93%20were%20yoked%20to%20the%20madressah%20curriculum.%20The%20classless%20education%20he%20promised%20remains%20a%20mirage%20but%20education%20standards%20plummeted.%20The%20upcoming%20generation%20is%20being%20stuffed%20with%20religious%20materials%20but%20knows%20no%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20minds%20of%20his%20blinded%20followers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20who%20see%20the%20United%20States%20as%20the%20incarnation%20of%20evil%2C%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20ouster%20was%20an%20American%20conspiracy.%20At%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20March%202022%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1682104%5C%22%3Ewaved%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%E2%80%98secret%E2%80%99%20document%20that%20supposedly%20was%20iron-clad%20proof%20of%20America%20calling%20for%20his%20eviction.%20But%20weeks%20later%2C%20he%20absolved%20America%20of%20blame%20while%20broadening%20the%20net%20of%20conspirators%20to%20include%20%E2%80%98Super-King%E2%80%99%20Bajwa%20(whose%20tenure%20had%20been%20extended)%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20Asif%20Zardari%2C%20and%20Maulana%20Fazlur%20Rehman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20victory%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%2C%20a%20well-known%20political%20commentator%20from%20India%20known%20for%20Pakistan-friendly%20views%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fcolumns%2FMani-Shankar-Aiyar%2F2024%2F02%2F24%2Fpak-army-defeated-again.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcitedly%20declared%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CFebruary%208%2C%202024%2C%20will%20be%20chalked%20up%20as%20the%20historic%20day%20on%20which%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20defeated%20their%20army.%E2%80%9D%20Given%20that%20the%20establishment%20indeed%20sought%20to%20vanquish%20Khan%2C%20is%20this%20really%20true%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20superficial%20level%2C%20yes.%20Many%20PTI%20supporters%20did%20vote%20against%20the%20generals.%20Their%20anti-army%20sentiment%20surfaced%20on%20May%209%20when%20they%20attacked%20and%20burned%20military%20facilities.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Khan%20has%20never%20expressed%20dismay%20at%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20business%2C%20commercial%2C%20and%20real-estate%20interests%20nor%20opposed%20appointments%20of%20retired%20army%20officers%20to%20top%20administrative%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20the%20army%20are%2C%20to%20quote%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1517563%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20same%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20His%20differences%20remain%20personal%20%E2%80%93%20some%20generals%20are%20for%20him%2C%20others%20against.%20Only%20animals%2C%20he%20famously%20declared%2C%20can%20be%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20election%20fulfils%20its%20purpose%20when%20it%20helps%20establish%20a%20representative%20government%3B%20enhances%20ability%20to%20deal%20with%20issues%20such%20as%20employment%20and%20allocation%20of%20resources%3B%20and%20brings%20forth%20individuals%20committed%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20decency%20and%20public%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20re-emergence%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20these%20ideals%2C%20suggesting%20political%20maturity%20remains%20a%20distant%20goal%20for%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPervez%20Hoodbhoy%20is%20an%20Islamabad-based%20physicist%20and%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1818493%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20appeared%20in%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Dawn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709567979000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12140453%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-12-at-1.53.46-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwhy-imran-khans-resurrection-does-not-promise-political-maturity-in-pakistan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Khan%20has%20never%20expressed%20dismay%20at%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20business%2C%20commercial%2C%20and%20real-estate%20interests%20nor%20opposed%20appointments%20of%20retired%20army%20officers%20to%20top%20administrative%20positions.%20He%20and%20the%20army%20are%2C%20to%20quote%20him%2C%20'on%20the%20same%20page'.%20His%20differences%20remain%20personal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fwhy-imran-khans-resurrection-does-not-promise-political-maturity-in-pakistan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20moment%20I%20met%