2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20bank%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsbi-requests-supreme-court-to-extend-time-till-june-30-to-furnish-electoral-bonds-information-251219%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Easked%20for%20time%20until%20June%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20citing%20difficulties%20in%20following%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20original%20deadline%20of%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20SBI%20said%20that%2022%2C217%20bonds%20had%20been%20issued%20to%20various%20political%20parties%20between%20April%202019%20and%20February%2015%20this%20year%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20the%20period%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20specified%20in%20its%20order%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20redeemed%20bonds%20were%20gradually%20mailed%20by%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20authorised%20branches%20to%20its%20main%20branch%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20added%20that%20because%20there%20were%20two%20%E2%80%98information%20silos%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20had%20to%20compile%2044%2C434%20sets%20of%20information%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20was%20brought%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%20early%202018.%20Through%20it%2C%20companies%20and%20individuals%20in%20India%20could%20make%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20February%2015%20order%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20electoral%20bonds%20violated%20voters%E2%80%99%20fundamental%20right%20to%20information%20and%20ordered%20the%20SBI%20to%20stop%20issuing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20ordered%20the%20bank%20to%20furnish%20the%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20between%20an%20interim%20order%20it%20issued%20on%20April%2012%2C%202019%20and%20the%20date%20of%20its%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20details%20must%20include%20the%20date%20the%20bonds%20were%20purchased%20on%2C%20the%20names%20of%20who%20purchased%20them%20and%20the%20bonds%E2%80%99%20denominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20ordered%20the%20bank%20to%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20bonds%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20concerned%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelevant%20details%20must%20include%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20date%20of%20encashment%20and%20the%20denomination%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20was%20ordered%20to%20publish%20on%20its%20website%20by%20March%2013%20the%20information%20given%20to%20it%20by%20the%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fbiz-tech%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2Fsbi-issues-electoral-bonds-worth-rs-16518-crore-in-30-tranches.html%5C%22%3ERs%2016%2C518%20crore%20worth%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20sold%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%202018%20to%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20the%20government%20recently%20informed%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20reading%20out%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20financial%20contributions%20to%20political%20parties%20are%20made%20either%20to%20support%20them%20or%20in%20fulfilment%20of%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements%2C%20referring%20to%20contributions%20being%20made%20in%20exchange%20for%20something%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20court%20stressed%20that%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20of%20political%20affiliation%20does%20not%20extend%20to%20contributions%20made%20to%20influence%20public%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709562401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04200200%2F3076973126_ab45efee1b_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fstate-bank-of-india-extra-time-june-30-electoral-bonds-supreme-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bank%20cited%20difficulties%20in%20following%20the%20court's%20original%20deadline%20of%20March%206%20and%20said%20it%20had%20to%20process%2044%2C434%20sets%20of%20information%20regarding%20bonds%20bought%20and%20encashed%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20LiveLaw%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fstate-bank-of-india-extra-time-june-30-electoral-bonds-supreme-court%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Free%20isn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20for%20Spotify%2C%20they%20want...'%3A%20Apple%20slams%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709561580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108211604%2Cimgsize-54362.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fapple-slams-spotify-free-isnt-enough-for-spotify-they-want-to-bend-rules-too%2Farticleshow%2F108211492.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20criticizes%20European%20Commission's%20%242%20billion%20fine%20on%20Spotify%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20lacking%20evidence%20of%20consumer%20harm.%20Apple%20claims%20Spotify%20rewrote%20App%20Store%20rules%20to%20its%20advantage%2C%20highlights%20developers%20not%20paying%20commission%2C%20engineering%20support%2C%20and%20plans%20to%20appeal%20for%20a%20safer%20App%20Store.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fapple-slams-spotify-free-isnt-enough-for-spotify-they-want-to-bend-rules-too%2Farticleshow%2F108211492.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Crores%20Lie%20Unclaimed%20in%20Demat%20Accounts%20of%20Indians%20Who%20Pass%20Away!%20How%20to%20Safeguard%20Your%20Savings%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20face%20it.%20None%20of%20us%20can%20foresee%20what%E2%80%99s%20waiting%20around%20the%20bend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsuring%20your%20loved%20ones%20are%20safeguarded%20in%20case%20of%20any%20unforeseen%20circumstances%20is%20paramount.%20Yet%2C%20shockingly%2C%20many%20overlook%20a%20simple%20yet%20crucial%20step%3A%20adding%20nominations%20to%20all%20their%20investments%2C%20bank%20accounts%2C%20and%20insurance%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20merely%20about%20streamlining%20matters%20for%20your%20beneficiaries%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20safeguarding%20your%20hard-earned%20money%20from%20being%20lost%20and%20ensuring%20it%20remains%20rightfully%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20truly%20astonishing%20is%20the%20significant%20amount%20of%20unclaimed%20assets%20currently%20lying%20idle%20in%20demat%20accounts%2C%20mutual%20funds%2C%20and%20insurance%20policies%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20nomination.%20Estimated%20to%20be%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%2080%2C000%20crore%2C%20this%20massive%20amount%20has%20no%20home%20to%20go%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20problem%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298273%2Fsebi-consultation-paper-green-debt-securities-invest-in-sustainable-finance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEBI%3C%2Fa%3E)%20has%20published%20a%20consultation%20paper%20on%20easing%20the%20nominations%20for%20your%20Demat%20accounts%20and%20other%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20nomination%20is%20important%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncluding%20nominees%20in%20demat%20accounts%20is%20indispensable%20in%20ensuring%20the%20seamless%20transfer%20of%20securities%2C%20such%20as%20shares%2C%20bonds%2C%20and%20mutual%20funds%2C%20in%20the%20unfortunate%20event%20of%20the%20account%20holder%E2%80%99s%20demise.%20This%20vital%20step%20ensures%20that%20the%20transmission%20of%20these%20securities%20is%20smooth%20and%20without%20risks.%20Consequently%2C%20it%20shields%20the%20investments%20made%20by%20the%20account%20holder%20from%20the%20possibility%20of%20being%20lost%20or%20entangled%20in%20legal%20quagmires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adding%20nominees%20to%20your%20accounts%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20simplifying%20matters%20for%20your%20beneficiaries%20%E2%80%94%20you%E2%80%99re%20also%20securing%20a%20brighter%2C%20more%20stable%20future%20for%20those%20you%20hold%20dear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fd3mygWN85TA%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fd3mygWN85TA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%20consultation%20paper%20by%20SEBI%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consultation%20paper%20by%20SEBI%20encapsulates%20close%20to%20all%20the%20potential%20doubts%20you%20may%20have%20concerning%20the%20nomination%20process%20for%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20examining%20its%20contents%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20a%20consultation%20paper%20is%20a%20document%20meant%20to%20spark%20discussion%20around%20policy%20proposals%20and%20ideas.%20Therefore%2C%20none%20of%20the%20points%20put%20forward%20by%20SEBI%20are%20binding%2C%20i.e.%20create%20a%20new%20law%20or%20policy.%20They%20are%20simply%20recommendations%20laid%20down%20for%20further%20conversation%20and%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20consultation%20paper%2C%20they%20broadly%20lay%20down%20three%20issues%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20the%20nomination%20process%20apply%20to%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20role%20of%20nominees%20with%20respect%20to%20legal%20heirs%20and%20wills%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20method%20of%20appointing%20nominees%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20very%20clearly%20underscored%20that%20nomination%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98entirely%20optional%20process%E2%80%99.%20The%20recommendation%20SEBI%20makes%20is%20that%20in%20a%20single%20person-held%20demat%20account%2C%20a%20clear%20declaration%20be%20made%20that%20they%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20assign%20a%20nominee.%20This%20is%20simply%20a%20measure%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20procedural%20ease%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20before%20reading%20the%20paper%20is%20the%20distinction%20between%20nominees%20and%20legal%20heirs%2C%20which%20can%20often%20be%20a%20point%20of%20confusion%20for%20a%20layperson.%20As%20highlighted%20by%20various%20financial%20experts%20and%20publications%2C%20nominees%20are%20not%20legal%20heirs%20to%20the%20securities.%20They%20are%20simply%20temporary%20custodians%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20the%20securities%20are%20correctly%20transferred%20to%20the%20legal%20heirs%2C%20as%20per%20a%20will%20or%20law.%20They%20are%20akin%20to%20an%20executor%20of%20a%20will%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20but%20for%20a%20specific%20asset%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20paper%2C%20SEBI%20provides%20suggestions%20on%20processes%20for%20how%20nominees%20can%20be%20appointed%20and%20how%20they%20must%20act.%20Nominees%20can%20be%20appointed%20through%20digital%20methods%20for%20ease%2C%20however%2C%20safety%20is%20kept%20in%20mind%20in%20this%20process%20as%20well%20by%20ensuring%20the%20requirement%20of%20a%20digital%20signature%20or%20Aadhaar-based%20eSigns.%20One%20needs%20to%20provide%20identification%20of%20the%20proposed%20nominee(s)%20as%20well.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20physical%20nomination%20through%20thumb%20impressions%20and%20verification%20also%20continues%20to%20be%20proposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20provides%20various%20scenarios%2C%20such%20as%20sole%20accounts%2C%20joint%20accounts%2C%20simultaneous%20deaths%20of%20account%20holders%20among%20others%2C%20and%20how%20a%20nominee%20will%20be%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20account%20for%20the%20next%20steps%20in%20each%20case.%20It%20also%20lays%20down%20which%20legal%20heirs%20are%20entitled%20to%20the%20securities%20in%20cases%20of%20joint%20accounts%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20read%20a%20more%20detailed%20summary%20of%20the%20paper%2C%20and%20provide%20your%20feedback%20on%20it%20by%208%20March%2C%202024%2C%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F48w8AwO%5C%22%3ECivis%20Platform%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivis%20is%20a%20civic-tech%20organisation%20that%20aggregates%20and%20simplifies%20draft%20laws%20and%20policies%20that%20are%20open%20for%20public%20feedback%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20the%20process%20as%20simple%20for%20you%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consultation%20paper%20has%20been%20hosted%20with%20a%20summary%20that%20you%20can%20read%20in%20an%20accessible%20format%2C%20in%20both%20English%20and%20Hindi%2C%20and%20give%20your%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20written%20by%20the%20team%20at%20Civis.vote%2C%20a%20non-profit%20platform%20that%20works%20to%20build%20dialogue%20between%20governments%20and%20citizens%2C%20using%20technology%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20the%20two.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709561507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fd3mygWN85TA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343865%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20thousands%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20lying%20unclaimed%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20nominations%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20has%20put%20out%20a%20consultation%20paper%20on%20easing%20the%20nominee%20process%20for%20your%20Demat%20accounts%20and%20other%20securities%20in%20case%20of%20any%20adverse%20events.%20Here's%20what%20that%20means%20for%20you%20and%20the%20steps%20you%20can%20take%20to%20protect%20your%20assets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Civis%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343865%2Fsebisebi-consultation-paper-on-nominee-filing-and-protection-of-assets-demats-mutual-funds%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ayodhya%3A%20The%20Humble%20Pilgrim%20Has%20Taken%20a%20Back%20Seat%20Amid%20a%20Costly%20Makeover%20to%20Drive%20Religious%20Tourism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16165449%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-16-at-4.52.13-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mystique%20of%20religion%20flounders%20here%3B%20spirituality%20hurries%20to%20take%20a%20back%20seat%20in%20New%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20Ayodhya.%20Today%20the%20most%20striking%20visual%20of%20that%20ancient%20town%20where%20the%20devout%20have%20thronged%20for%20centuries%20can%20said%20to%20be%20unabashed%20contractor%20capitalism%20running%20hard%20to%20make%20it%20count%20in%20case%20the%20bubble%20bursts%20all%20too%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnseen%20hands%20of%20contractors%20and%20management%20from%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20appear%20to%20be%20just%20about%20everywhere%20in%20the%20jobs%20to%20be%20executed%2C%20overriding%20local%20sentiment%2C%20with%20the%20river%20Sarju%20as%20a%20mute%20witness.%20On%20its%20banks%20are%20now%20moored%20cruise%20boats%20for%20the%20anticipated%20rush%20of%20the%20fancy%20tourist%2C%20not%20the%20paddle%20boats%20of%20the%20humble%20Ke%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20tribe%20of%20fisherfolk%20and%20boatmen%20who%20once%20had%20the%20ear%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20the%20King%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%20suggests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20this%20cannot%20be%20formally%20acknowledged%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20plain%20that%20the%20sovereign%20body%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20not%20the%20government%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emahant%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20priest)%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20Sri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20or%20SRJTK.%20It%20is%20an%20autonomous%20body%20created%20in%202020%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guidance%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20of%20November%202019%20which%20handed%20over%20the%20title%20of%20the%20land%20under%20the%20demolished%20Babri%20mosque%20to%20the%20same%20set%20that%20was%20castigated%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20sharp%20terms%20for%20destroying%20the%20mosque.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20trust%20is%20charged%20with%20overseeing%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20around%20the%20site%20of%20the%20former%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20pulled%20down%20with%20human%20hands%20in%201992%20by%20surcharged%20mobs%20high%20on%20the%20opium%20of%20religion%20and%20guided%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20then%20top%20leadership.%20It%20is%20also%20entrusted%20with%20the%20improvement%20of%20Ayodhya%20with%20an%20eye%20to%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20Hindu%20Vatican%20or%20Mecca%20and%20a%20mammoth%20tourist%20attraction.%20Bulging%20tourism%20revenue%20is%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20and%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%E2%80%99s%20mind.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVHP%20vice-president%20Champat%20Rai%20is%20the%20SRJTK%20general%20secretary%20and%20calls%20the%20shots%20in%20the%20new%20temple%E2%80%99s%20management.%20The%20VHP%20is%20an%20affiliate%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20The%20most%20influential%20entity%20for%20Ayodhya%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20construction%20committee%20of%20the%20SRJTK%2C%20Nripendra%20Misra.%20He%20served%20as%20the%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20his%20first%20term%20and%20is%20now%20serving%2C%20in%20post-retirement%20capacity%2C%20a%20post%20of%20exceeding%20importance%20which%20involves%20dealing%20with%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20engineering%20and%20consultancy%20firms%20rather%20extensively.%20In%20effect%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20PMO%20runs%20Ayodhya%2C%20a%20very%20special%20project%20high%20on%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20ideological%20and%20potential%20revenue-index.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sums%20projected%20are%20impressive.%20According%20to%20a%20Mint%20report%20of%20January%2023%2C%20the%20brokerage%20Jefferies%20%E2%80%9Chas%20recently%20estimated%20that%20a%20%24%2010%20billion%20makeover%20of%20Ayodhya%20with%20a%20new%20airport%2C%20revamped%20railway%20station%2C%20township%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eroad%20connectivity%20will%20likely%20drive%20a%20multiplier%20effect%20with%20new%20hotels%20and%20other%20economic%20activities.%20It%20could%20attract%2050%20million%20tourists%20a%20year.%E2%80%9D%20Activities%20under%20the%20Ayodhya%20Masterplan%20have%20a%20time%20horizon%20that%20extends%20to%202031.%20Real%20estate%20is%20the%20name%20of%20the%20game.%20It%20has%20rarely%20had%20it%20so%20good.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20probably%20no%20way%20to%20test%20such%20an%20exuberant%20projection%2C%20but%20context%20helps.%20Agra%E2%80%99s%20world%20famous%20Taj%20Mahal%20nets%20some%20six%20million%20tourists%20annually%20in%20contrast%2C%20and%20there%20are%20other%20sites%20of%20historical%20and%20architectural%20wonder%20in%20its%20vicinity.%20If%20Ayodhya%20were%20to%20raise%20eight%20or%2010%20times%20that%20number%2C%20it%20will%20probably%20have%20to%20upstage%20the%20tourist%20arrivals%20of%20several%20leading%20international%20destinations%20taken%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelirium-over-ram-mandir-a-nation-consecrated-or-desecrated%5C%22%3EDelirium%20Over%20Ram%20Mandir%3A%20A%20Nation%20Consecrated%20or%20Desecrated%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFaizabad%20district%20%E2%80%93%20now%20renamed%20Ayodhya%20in%20a%20burst%20of%20religiosity%20%E2%80%93%20with%20its%20principal%20town%20of%20the%20same%20name%2C%20was%20the%20original%20seat%20of%20the%20Oudh%20(Awadh)%20nawabs%2C%20who%20later%20transferred%20themselves%20to%20Lucknow.%20The%20city%20thus%20has%20a%20flavour%20of%20that%20past.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20entire%20district%20and%20those%20around%20it%20constitute%20the%20agricultural%20hinterland%20of%20this%20region%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%20this%20backwater%2C%20industry%20(MSME%20and%20large%20included)%20has%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20under%20Rs%2025%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20relatively%20recent%20data%20of%20Union%20MSME%20ministry%2C%20and%20a%20workforce%20of%20about%2030%2C000.%20A%20generally%20poor%20area%20has%20been%20dragged%20into%20the%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Est%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%2C%20as%20is%20the%20story%20in%20most%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20a%20standalone%2C%20modern%20temple%20of%20a%20particular%20faith%2C%20thus%20lacking%20universal%20appeal%2C%20in%20a%20relatively%20less%20developed%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20sustain%20the%20massive%20multiplier%20effect%20projections%20that%20are%20based%20on%20international%20tourist%20arrivals%2C%20presumably%20made%20up%20in%20large%20measure%20of%20well-heeled%20NRIs%3F%20Fancy%20hotels%2C%20glittering%20airport%2C%20and%20a%20very%20modern%20large%20railway%20facility%2C%20in%20a%20backward%20region%20that%20may%20offer%20little%20demand%20support%2C%20appear%20somewhat%20incongruous.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20drummed%20up%20support%20to%20transport%20people%20to%20Ayodhya%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20in%20the%20weeks%20following%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20by%C2%A0%20Modi%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20buzz%20is%20that%20ruling%20party%20MPs%20ad%20MLAs%20have%20been%20assigned%20quotas%20to%20send%20to%20Ayodhya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20railways%20have%20laid%20out%20fast%20trains%20called%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAstha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(faith)%20specials.%20Many%20passengers%20seem%20genuinely%20simple%2C%20religious%20folk%2C%20others%20like%20mobilised%20political%20cadres.%20Members%20of%20a%20VHP%20group%20from%20western%20India%20said%20each%20of%20them%20paid%20Rs%201%2C800%2F-%20for%20the%20train%20journey%20both%20ways%20and%20one%20day%E2%80%99s%20stay%20in%20a%20comfortable%20tent%20city%2C%20erected%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20state-inspired%20religiosity.%20The%20railways%20have%20slashed%20all%20concessions%20in%20fares%2C%20including%20for%20senior%20citizens.%20But%20the%20neo-pilgrims%20mobilized%20for%20the%20Ayodhya%20campaign%20appear%20to%20have%20benefited%20from%20moderated%20fares.%20Hundreds%20of%20trains%20are%20expected%20to%20run%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProbably%20the%20most%20conspicuous%20local%20grumble%20this%20writer%20encountered%20during%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20Ayodhya%20concerned%20the%20contractors.%20Perhaps%20this%20was%20a%20more%20vocal%20grumble%20than%20the%20vociferous%20complaints%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes%20and%20small%20businesses%20bulldozed%20to%20widen%20roads%20in%20the%20entire%20temple%20complex%20of%20Ayodhya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20came%20across%20guards%20of%20a%20security%20company%20from%20Gujarat%20called%20%E2%80%9CKavach%E2%80%9D%20charged%20with%20managing%20a%20section%20of%20the%20river%20ghat.%20According%20to%20one%20complaint%2C%20even%20labour%20(who%20appeared%20to%20be%20tribal%20people)%20were%20transported%20from%20Gujarat%20to%20work%20on%20some%20cable-laying%20beneath%20roads.%20Has%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20exhausted%20its%20capacity%20to%20supply%20even%20the%20basics%20to%20mount%20an%20effort%20to%20modernise%20itself%3F%20The%20question%20and%20its%20implication%20hangs%20in%20the%20air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGuided%20to%20its%20final%20moments%20on%20January%2022%2C%20Modi%20inaugurated%20an%20unfinished%20temple%2C%20practically%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20national%20elections%2C%20with%20a%20rousing%20speech%20linking%20religion%20with%20nation%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20business%2C%20film%2C%20and%20sports%20stars.%20Those%20who%20were%20noticeably%20absent%20were%20the%20ordinary%20Ram%20devotees%20of%20the%20ancient%20town%20of%20Ayodhya.%20The%20project%20that%20surreptitiously%20commenced%20in%201949%20with%20the%20insertion%20of%20an%20idol%20of%20Ram%20inside%20a%20500-year%20old%20mosque%20was%20at%20last%20complete.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%20reminds%20us%20that%20Hitler%20too%20had%20ordered%20a%20%E2%80%9Cone%20thousand%20year%20Reich%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20But%20where%20does%20this%20leave%20Ram%3F%20This%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20small%20triumph%20for%20political%20Hinduism%20%E2%80%93%20the%20unveiling%20of%20the%20unfinished%20temple%2C%20touted%20in%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20convention%20in%20New%20Delhi%20last%20month%20as%20a%20singular%20%E2%80%9Cachievement%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20unleashing%20of%20the%20(doubtless%20Hindu)%20nation%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cconsciousness%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20harbinger%20of%20%E2%80%9Cone%20thousand%20years%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20story%20of%20Ram%20is%20traditionally%20cherished%20in%20every%20Hindu%20home.%20His%20love%20of%20all%20beings%2C%20his%20poise%20even%20in%20war%2C%20his%20thoughtfulness%20for%20his%20people%2C%20even%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20disregarding%20his%20wife%20Seeta%2C%20his%20glowing%20beauty%2C%20and%20the%20beauty%20of%20his%20actions%20which%20gets%20culturally%20underlined%20as%20the%20metric%20for%20performance%20of%20duty%2C%20are%20celebrated%20as%20popular%20theatre%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamaleela%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20across%20the%20villages%2C%20towns%20and%20cities%20of%20North%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recognition%20of%20this%2C%20the%20Muslim%20poet%20and%20future%20philosopher%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20Mohammed%20Iqbal%2C%20had%20given%20on%20Ram%20the%20title%20of%20Imam-e-Hind.%20That%20Ram%20appears%20to%20have%20gone%20missing%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20the%20time%20of%20Modi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pilgrim%2C%20the%20true%20Ram%20devotee%2C%20apt%20to%20have%20been%20brought%20up%20to%20conjure%20the%20gentle%2C%20almost%20boy-like%2C%20divine%20image%20of%20Ram%20in%20the%20manner%20made%20immortal%20by%20the%20sage%20Valmiki%20in%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamayan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(probably%20around%202000%20years%20ago)%2C%20or%20the%20much%20later%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Goswami%20Tulsi%20Das%20(late%2016%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century)%2C%20stands%20stupefied%20by%20the%20sights%20and%20high-decibel%20tawdry%20sounds%20of%20a%20construction%20and%20religious%20tourist%20capitalism%20in%20the%20first%20gear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20article%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeity%20to%20Crusader%3A%20The%20Changing%20Iconography%20of%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20theatre%20scholar%20Anuradha%20Kapur%20writes%3A%20%E2%80%9CIcons%20seek%20to%20represent%20what%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20essential%20features%20of%20a%20deity.%20Traditional%20iconography%20tended%20to%20represent%20Ram%2C%20Janani%20and%20Lakshman%20smiling%20serenely.%20Emblematically%2C%20the%20figures%20represented%20tranquility%2C%20compassion%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Eshanta%20rasa.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20images%20now%20available%E2%80%A6Whatever%20else%20it%20might%20be%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Erasa%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20these%20images%20is%20not%20shanta%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BBut%5D%20so%20far%20as%20iconographical%20features%20are%20concerned%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20commonalities%20of%20representation%E2%80%A6..what%20these%20several%20Rams%20share%20are%20the%20attributes%20of%20a%20sympathetic%20god%2C%20attributes%20which%20are%20his%20alone%E2%80%A6.he%20is%20serene%20and%20ever-forgiving%3B%20he%20is%20ever-youthful%2C%20boyish%20almost%2C%20with%20a%20conspicuous%20lack%20of%20masculine%20power%3B%20and%20yet%2C%20he%20is%20the%20lord%20of%20the%20universe%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Emaryada%20purushottam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pilgrim%20cannot%20but%20also%20regard%20with%20some%20anxiety%20%E2%80%93%20and%20with%20thoughts%20of%C2%A0%20deviation%20from%20the%20path%20%E2%80%93%20the%20New%20Ram%20in%20the%20New%20Ayodhya%20of%20New%20India%2C%20presented%20on%20the%20new%20walls%20as%20murals%20depicting%20a%20ferocious%20Hindu%20warrior%2C%20possibly%20even%20a%20hunter%2C%20the%20defender%20of%20a%20ferocious%20nationalism.%20In%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Est%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20India%2C%20is%20Ram%20going%20to%20be%20cyclostyled%20as%20a%20politician%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%20is%20a%20political%20commentator%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709560751000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16165449%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-16-at-4.52.13-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fayodhya-the-humble-pilgrim-has-taken-a-back-seat-amid-a-costly-makeover-to-drive-religious-tourism%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pilgrim%2C%20the%20true%20Ram%20devotee%2C%20stands%20stupefied%20by%20the%20sights%20and%20high-decibel%20tawdry%20sounds%20of%20a%20construction%20and%20religious%20tourist%20capitalism%20in%20the%20first%20gear.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A137%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fayodhya-the-humble-pilgrim-has-taken-a-back-seat-amid-a-costly-makeover-to-drive-religious-tourism%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JetBlue%2C%20Spirit%20Ending%20%243.8%20Billion%20Merger%20Plan%20After%20Federal%20Judge%20Blocked%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Justice%20Department%20sued%20to%20block%20the%20merger%20last%20year%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20reduce%20competition%20and%20drive%20up%20fares%2C%20especially%20for%20travelers%20who%20depend%20on%20low-fare%20Spirit.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709560564000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65e5d2092300003100656557.jpeg%3Fcache%3DiqZixkhtww%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fjetblue-spirit-airlines-end-proposed-merger-deal_n_65e5d1f9e4b0d2a2475a2f31%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Justice%20Department%20sued%20to%20block%20the%20merger%20