CBesides%20using%20photovoltaic%20panels%20and%20solar%20water%20heaters%2C%20all%20the%20meals%20are%20served%20in%20disposable%20and%20compostable%20leaf%20plates%2C%20and%20we%20offer%20a%20sustainable%20and%20responsible%20laundry%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20compost%20all%20their%20wet%20waste%20which%20is%20later%20used%20in%20their%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20food%20that%20our%20guests%20eat%20is%20sourced%20from%20our%20organic%20fields%2C%20which%20cultivate%20vegetables%2C%20cereals%2C%20pulses%2C%20oilseeds%2C%20and%20more.%20We%20refrain%20from%20using%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20ensuring%20that%20all%20crops%20are%20grown%20naturally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20encourage%20travellers%2C%20whenever%20possible%2C%20to%20participate%20in%20non-polluting%20activities%20such%20as%20walks%2C%20cycling%20and%20camel%20cart%20excursions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20keep%20their%20promotion%20activities%20in%20line%20with%20their%20philosophy%2C%20the%20eco-stay%E2%80%99s%20business%20cards%2C%20cookery%20books%2C%20and%20brochures%20on%20hand-made%20recycled%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Guests%20can%20enjoy%20craft%20workshops%20including%20tie-dye%2C%20bangle%20making%2C%20pottery%2C%20Mandala%20drawing%20etc%20at%20the%20eco-lodge.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frajasthan-2-1709299575-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads