wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETowards%20a%20landfill-free%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20pursuing%20engineering%20at%20Vignana%20Bharathi%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Pavani%20was%20part%20of%20a%20student%20forum%20called%20%E2%80%98Eco%20Club%E2%80%99%20that%20stressed%20on%20awareness%20about%20sustainability%20and%20adopting%20eco-friendly%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20we%20went%20to%20a%20nearby%20village%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20efficiently%20segregating%20waste.%20When%20we%20asked%20villagers%20why%20they%20preferred%20dumping%20waste%20instead%20of%20segregating%20it%20at%20the%20household%20level%2C%20they%20said%20it%20anyway%20ended%20up%20getting%20mixed%20in%20landfills%20so%20what%20was%20the%20use%20of%20segregation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20everyone%20forgot%20the%20incident%20after%20coming%20back%20to%20college%2C%20Pavani%20wondered%20how%20to%20solve%20the%20issue.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20build%20a%20machine%20where%20segregated%20waste%20could%20be%20dumped%20at%20the%20household%20level%3F%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2026-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-1-1709301234.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pavani%20understood%20that%20while%20organic%20waste%20was%20a%20problem%2C%20it%20could%20also%20be%20turned%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-1-1709301234.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-1-1709301234-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-1-1709301234-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-1-1709301234-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fvapra-1-1709301234-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343680%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPavani%20understood%20that%20while%20organic%20waste%20was%20a%20problem%2C%20it%20could%20also%20be%20turned%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20her%20final%20year%20of%20college%2C%20she%20encountered%20a%20rather%20major%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CAmidst%20the%20conversation%20of%20tackling%20plastic%20waste%2C%20we%20overlook%20the%20issues%20brought%20down%20by%20organic%20waste.%20About%2060%20percent%20of%20waste%20at%20home%20comprises%20organic%20waste%20that%20is%20dumped%20recklessly%20in%20landfills.%20Over%20time%2C%20this%20organic%20waste%20breaks%20down%20and%20releases%20methane%20gas%20emissions%20leading%20to%20global%20warming%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20people%20in%20urban%20spaces%20spend%20a%20lot%20on%20purchasing%20organic%20fertilisers%20as%20not%20everyone%20can%20prepare%20compost%20at%20home%20because%20of%20its%20complex%20process.%20You%20have%20to%20keep%20putting%20kitchen%20waste%20and%20soil%20in%20layers.%20It%20also%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%20as%20it%20takes%20weeks%20to%20prepare%20the%20compost%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavani%20understood%20that%20while%20organic%20waste%20was%20a%20problem%2C%20it%20could%20also%20be%20turned%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20In%202020%2C%20she%20came%20up%20with%20an%20innovative%20composter%20that%20not%20only%20solved%20the%20everyday%20dumping%20of%20organic%20waste%20but%20also%20aimed%20at%20making%20composting%20people%E2%80%99s%20daily%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20year%2C%20she%20co-founded%20%E2%8