%2Ftruth-social-founders-sue-trump-shares_n_65e0e296e4b013678e1468b5%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Mobile%20Creche%20Cares%20For%20Kids%20of%20Migrant%20Labourers%20Till%20They%20Are%2018%2C%20Helps%20Them%20Get%20Stable%20Jobs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20thousands%20of%20migrant%20workers%20leave%20the%20comforts%20of%20their%20homes%20to%20move%20to%20other%20cities%20in%20search%20of%20livelihood.%20Amid%20the%20sounds%20of%20sledge%20hammers%20and%20bulldozers%2C%20their%20young%20children%20are%20exposed%20to%20child%20labour%2C%20poor%20academic%20achievements%2C%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20expected%20to%20provide%20daycare%20facilities%20to%20these%20children%20of%20migrant%20labourers%20at%20the%20construction%20sites%20but%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Edai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Emausi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20hired%20to%20look%20after%20these%20children.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20these%20women%20lack%20skills%20or%20training%20to%20give%20attention%20to%20the%20nurturing%20and%20growth%20of%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manjusha%20Doshi%2C%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20Tara%20Mobile%20Creches%20Pune%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20ignorance%20at%20the%20parent%20level%20as%20they%20get%20busy%20in%20their%20construction%20work.%20If%20they%20leave%20the%20work%2C%20then%20they%20lose%20their%20daily%20wages%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20commendable%20move%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20has%20set%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F2221%2Fmobile-creches-caring-for-children-of-construction-workers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emobile%20cr%C3%A8che-and-daycare%20centres%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20the%20construction%20site%20so%20the%20mothers%20could%20safely%20leave%20their%20children%20involved%20in%20acti